# game/day 15.rpy:88
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_759fa6ad:

    # "Nn-, Shun-kun's calling me for breakfast.\nIt's a very pleasant awakening for my half-asleep head.\nI face my posture up as I reflect upon that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 118-120)
    "嗯，早上被峻君叫起来吃早餐啊。[l] 这对于还处在睡眠中的大脑来说是很好的清醒方式啊。[l] [漏れ]就这样以仰躺着的方式开始想着。"

# game/day 15.rpy:89
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_3a5a3fc3:

    # fn "「Shun-kun, you know, I have a small request for you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 122-123)
    fn "「峻君，那个啊，有件事情想拜托你。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:93
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_d0891a3b:

    # su "「What is it-?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 128-129)
    su "「什么事？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:94
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_a85c29bf:

    # fn "「It seems I'm not fully awake yet,\n so I'm going to ask for your cooperation.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 131-133)
