# game/day 15.rpy:146
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_62d891c8:

    # su "「Oh, Shin-san...\n [fn]-san wanted me to wake him up this way.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 224-226)
    su "「啊，深桑……[l] [博行]桑希望我这样子叫他起床。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:147
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_2b4c4b0f:

    # "Shun-kun looks up as he's thrusting his waist on me,\nand Shin-kun glares at me with eyes full of contempt.\nThis kind of play is great."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 228-230)
    "在仰躺的[漏れ]的腰上摇动自己身体的峻君。[l] 接着是用那轻蔑的眼光朝着这个方向看的深君。[l] 这场游戏达到了最高潮。"

# game/day 15.rpy:148
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_2084cfb8:

    # "My unsuspecting childhood friend is being decieved,\nrocking on top of the crotch of his suspicious partner.\nSo when Shin said that and pierced me with his gaze,"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 232-234)
    "欺骗了什么都不懂的幼驯染， 笑着让其坐在自己跨下摇动的可疑人物。[l] 仿佛是这么说着的深君的视线狠狠地刺向[漏れ]。"

# game/day 15.rpy:149
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_2f594c3e:

    # "A chill and an\noverflowing feeling of self-admonition\nruns through my body."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 236-238)
    "在[漏れ]的身体内同时有着 持续而来的兴奋感与 把事情搞砸了而产生的自我规律感。"

# game/day 15.rpy:153
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_e8910157:

    # si "「...Well, whatever.\n The food is going to be gone, but see if I care.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 242-244)
    si "「……算了，随便你们。[l] 吃的东西什么时候会吃完我可不知道喔。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:157
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_63da5821:

    # "Shin-kun turns around and leaves.{w} Aah, {w=.2}if it would have been Torahiko, he would have mounted me too,{w} or if it was Juuichi-san he would have mounted me as a form of punishment."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 249-251)
    "深君转过头去就离开了帐篷。[l] 啊啊，[wdt]如果是虎彦的话应该会跟着一起坐上来吧， 如果是柔一的话应该是会带有制裁感觉的坐上来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:158
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_cc44ec0c:

    # "If it was Tatsu-nii... a tail bashing!{p}That would have been enough to completely crush me flat."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 253-254)
    "辰树的话……碰！[wdt]　这样子的 就把[漏れ]给压死吧。[l]"

# game/day 15.rpy:159
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_1940f548:

    # "If it was Kyouji and Soutarou-kun, they would have done the same thing next to us... {w=.3}No."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 255)
    "京慈和宗太郎君的话应该会在旁边做相同的……没这种事吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:160
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_fbcb2529:

    # "If it was Kounosuke, he would have been taking a flurry of pictures, which I guess I was prepared for happening anyways."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 257-258)
    "如果是孝之助的话一定要有觉悟， 他会拍下照片到处去宣传吧。[l]"

# game/day 15.rpy:161
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_746d4a46:

    # "So in comparison, I think I was lucky that it was Shin-kun that saw us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 259)
    "跟那些人比起来被深君看到应该是算幸运的吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:162
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_d85e79fb:

    # "...I'll come up with a shoddy excuse later."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 267)
    "……虽然可能是很烂的辩解但是等一下还是去找他说明吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:166
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_f87279b5:

    # su "「[fn]-san, did that wake you up?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 272-273)
    su "「[博行]桑，你醒了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:167
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_7fcd4fe6:

    # "His wagging tail brushes against my feet.\nI'm sorry for toying with him while he was unaware of it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 275-276)
    "毛绒绒的尾巴触碰到[漏れ]的脚。[l] 抱歉啊，玩弄了什么都不懂的峻君。"

# game/day 15.rpy:168
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_8617c07f:

    # "An unintentional transformation in my head had caused me\nto simulate that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 278-279)
    "在脑内模拟了转换过的 最理想的起床方式。"

# game/day 15.rpy:169
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_9edffa28:

    # fn "「Thank you, Shun-kun! Now, let's go get something to eat!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 281-282)
    fn "「谢谢你啊峻君！[wdt]　好了[漏れ]们去吃饭吧！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:170
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_shun_2b81c5ee:

    # su "「Okay-!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 284-285)
    su "「好！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:181
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_7f0aff1c:

    # who "「Hey...{w} Hey, [fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 302-303)
    who "「喂……喂、[博行]」"

# game/day 15.rpy:182
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_df8874f8:

    # "In my half-asleep consciousness, I can hear a voice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 305)
    "半梦半醒之间，听到了那个声音。"

# game/day 15.rpy:183
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_6f063354:

    # who "「Hey, wake up.\n It's already morning.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 307-309)
    who "「喂，差不多该起来了。[l] 已经早上了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:184
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_9bf88067:

    # fn "「Uuh... Mm?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 311-312)
    fn "「唔……嗯？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:185
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_e857f38f:

    # "At those words, I open my eyes reflexively.\nBut my vision is blurry and I can't see anything."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 314-315)
    "听到了谁在说话，[漏れ]条件反射地睁开了眼睛。[l] 但是视线还很模糊所以看不清楚。"

# game/day 15.rpy:186
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_6b4264ef:

    # "I try my best to look around,\nbut I'm unsuccessful because of the bright sunshine."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 317-318)
    "虽然努力地尝试看清， 但是阳光太过晃眼所以不是很顺利。"

# game/day 15.rpy:187
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_d11e0a8a:

    # fn "「Mm? Morning...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 320-321)
    fn "「嗯？[wdt]　早上吗……？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:188
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_5879be34:

    # "With my eyes half-closed, I try to sit up.\nIs my body still asleep?\nIt's not usually this difficult to move."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 323-325)
    "总之先以半张开眼的状态坐起上半身。[l] 是身体还在沉睡的状态吗， 平时很简单的动作现在作起来却异常辛苦。"

# game/day 15.rpy:189
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_9a747a4d:

    # who "「You're finally getting up.\n ...No, still asleep?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 327-329)
    who "「终于起来了吗。[l] ――不，还在睡吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:190
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_6edb0de8:

    # fn "「...No, I'm getti-uaaa!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 331-332)
    fn "「……不，已经起来了！？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:191
translate chinese_simplified camp15_wakeup_kouya_f5428580:

    # "Before I can finish speaking,\nsomething cold covers my face,\nthen begins to wipe roughly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 334-336)
    "在[漏れ]完全说完之前， 有什么冰冷的东西盖在了脸上。[l] 于是就那样开始擦拭着[漏れ]的脸。"

# game/day 15.rpy:192
