# game/day 15.rpy:1052
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shun_697c64c7:

    # su "「Yes!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 1801)
    su "「好！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1063
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_49c4de3f:

    # fn "「Kouya, what are going to do?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2200)
    fn "「洸哉要做什么呢？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1064
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_52d97dc3:

    # "For now, I'll ask Kouya,\nsince he's closest to me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2203)
    "总之，先听听最近的洸哉的意见吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1068
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_6c7fbbf0:

    # ka "「Well... First I was going to hang around here.\n I've kind of been looking for something.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2208)
    ka "「是呢……\n总之我想去那边逛逛。\n有点东西想找。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1069
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0455913d:

    # fn "「Looking for something...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2213)
    fn "「要找的东西……？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1070
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_59884a8c:

    # ka "「Well, it's nothing big,\n but I don't have anything in particular to do.\n I just thought I'd kill some time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2216)
    ka "「啊，虽然不是什么了不起的东西，\n不过也没有其他事好做了。\n我认为正好拿来打发时间。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1071
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_84a584c0:

    # "?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2221)
    "「？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1072
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a833bdab:

    # "I don't really understand what he's on about.\nHe said he's looking for something,\nbut he doesn't know what he's looking for."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2224)
    "[漏れ]不是很理解洸哉话的意思。\n他像是想要找什么东西，\n不过看起来他自己也不知道那东西是什么。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1073
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_db2f2b24:

    # "But hearing him say something so\nmysterious raises my interest.\nIt piques my curiosity."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2228)
    "但是，\n就是听到这样意味深长的话把[漏れ]的兴趣勾引出来了。\n总觉得热情高涨起来了呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1074
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_c362a7af:

    # "What could Kouya be looking for\nin the great outdoors!?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2232)
    "洸哉要找的东西到底是什么呢？\n在这样的大自然中！"

# game/day 15.rpy:1075
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d8ef4c61:

    # "Everybody else also seems to be a little interested,\nthey're showing a sense of wordless wonder."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2235)
    "其他的人似乎也有点在意，\n露出一副无言的感叹的样子。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1079
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_2431c5ab:

    # si "「...So, how is this going to end up?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2241)
    si "「……所以，最后决定了吗，之后做什么？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1080
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_086fa8d3:

    # "In the middle of this, Shin-kun's\ncold voice drops down on us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2244)
    "在当中的深的冷静的声音。\n本来已经忘记的问题回到脑海中。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1081
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b30d09cd:

    # "I return to the question\nthat I had completely forgotten."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2245)
    "本来已经忘记的问题回到脑海中。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1082
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e351384c:

    # "Then everybody lets out a groan at the same time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2247)
    "于是全体成员，都发出了苦恼的呻吟。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1086
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d934406d:

    # ta "「Ah, it's already too much trouble!\n All right, now it's free time!\n Everybody go do whatever you want!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2252)
    ta "「啊，麻烦死了！\n好吧，那接下来就自由行动好了！\n可以去做自己想做的事！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1087
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_9a873d97:

    # "Since he's the oldest,\nTatsu-nii has the voice of authority."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2257)
    "那边的年龄最大的辰兄一锤定音。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1088
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_81e93512:

    # "There are no objections, only words of agreement."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2258)
    "谁也没有反对这个意见，大家都赞同了这个提议。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1089
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_8973fcb1:

    # "Eventually, his words of command\nsmoothly put an end to the conversation."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2260)
    "最后，讨论就在他的号令下结束了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1093
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_25099483:

    # ta "「But!{p} Keep an eye on the time for coming back!{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2264)
    ta "「但——是——！\n请看好回来的时间！\n"

# game/day 15.rpy:1095
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_88f930b2:

    # extend "That is all!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2267)
    extend "就是这样！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1102
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_1ba51e8a:

    # "At Tatsu-nii's orders, everybody\nscatters and begins to move."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2279)
    "听过辰兄的号令，大家开始四散而开做自己的事情。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1103
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_8e4b8646:

    # "Going to the outdoor bath, reading a book,\nor looking around, it seems everybody has already\ndecided what they're going to do."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2280)
    "有去露天温泉的，有读书的，有去探险的，\n看起来大家都有了自己的决定。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1104
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_60fcdc1e:

    # "What should I do?\nI'm used to thinking about the scene,\nbut now there's no need for that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2283)
    "[漏れ]要做什么呢。\n虽然总是陷入要思考这个问题的情况，不过这次看来没有必要了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1105
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_670589ac:

    # "What Kouya was talking about\nearlier still hasn't left my head."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2286)
    "刚才洸哉所说的话。还留在脑海里不曾离开。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1106
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_daa8b380:

    # "The more I think about it, the more it bothers me.\nIt just makes me even more curious."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2287)
    "越考虑就越是在意。\n好奇心也不断地增加。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1107
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_501c7288:

    # "In an instant, I'm filled with that feeling,\nand I can't resist anymore."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2290)
    "对于瞬间填满心中的那个感觉，\n[漏れ]已经不知道如何抵抗了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1108
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ecb0dbe1:

    # "There's only one choice in my mind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2292)
    "连考虑的余地都没有，在心中已经只剩下这个选项了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1109
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_5712f646:

    # "From time to time, people come across\na box with unknown contents,\nand now there is one such box in front of me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2294)
    "就像人们总是想打开一个未知的箱子得知其中的内容，\n而现在，[漏れ]的眼前就有这样一个谜之箱子。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1110
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_606874c2:

    # "If that's the case, then I have\nno choice but to open it, right?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2297)
    "这样的话，除了打开它没有其他办法了吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1111
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_6945dc55:

    # "So, this is the negotiation phase..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2299)
    "所以说，交涉阶段――"

# game/day 15.rpy:1112
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_24c9a59d:

    # fn "「Hey, Kouya. What you were talking about earlier...\n Can I come along too?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2301)
    fn "「呐，洸哉。刚才所说的那件事……\n让[漏れ]跟去可以吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1113
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f3f6102e:

    # "I'm going to search for that thing, too.\nI walked up to Kouya to start talking."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2305)
    "[漏れ]边提着边抓住了开始向「想要找的东西」\n出发的洸哉的背。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1117
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b2f89fef:

    # ka "「Oh, it doesn't matter to me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2311)
    ka "「啊，无所谓啦。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1118
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_103456b7:

    # "Mission Complete!\nThat was easy."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2314)
    "――Mission Complete！\n这么简单啊。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1122
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ae4da1b0:

    # ka "「But I don't know whether or not we'll find it,\n there's a possiblity we won't.\n You aren't going to complain?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2319)
    ka "「但是还不知道能不能找到，\n即使找到了也有可能什么都没有。\n即使这样也不抱怨吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1123
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d22b34ea:

    # fn "「Yeah, that's okay.\n We'll think about it when we get to it,\n let's just do this for the memories.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2324)
    fn "「嗯，没关系。\n要是有那样的时候，把它当作一种回忆就好了。\n那样子也很快乐啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1124
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a3b5a52f:

    # fn "「Besides, it'll be fun too!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2329)
    fn "[漏れ]现在说出来的话真好啊。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1125
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_14014b94:

    # "I said something nice just now.\nIf I just increased the tension,\nI wouldn't hesitate to congratulate myself."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2329)
    "[漏れ]现在说出来的话真好啊。\n是现在情绪正高涨的[漏れ]的话，\n即使沾沾自喜也是毫不迟疑地。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1129
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3be1c01d:

    # ka "「Yeah, you're right about that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2335)
    ka "「嘛，说得也是呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1130
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_261582c1:

    # "He just quickly brushed away my wise words."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2338)
    "可是[漏れ]的名言被轻巧地避开了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1131
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a4e475ff:

    # "...Well, he usually does that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2340)
    "……不过，这也是经常发生的事。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1132
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_dee4f1cb:

    # fn "「Yeah... Hmmm.\n So, what are we looking for?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2342)
    fn "「唔……对了。\n那个是什么？　要找什么呢？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1136
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a709a9ad:

    # ka "「That's a secret.\n If you come with me,\n you might find out!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2349)
    ka "「是秘密。\n你跟过来大概就明白了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1137
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_94ac75a8:

    # "Kouya gives a mischievous smile,\nand briskly walks off."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2353)
    "洸哉恶作剧似地笑了笑，飞快地开始走了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1141
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4c75ee4f:

    # fn "「Huh? Come on, tell me!\n Hey, wait up-!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2358)
    fn "「诶，告诉[漏れ]一下也没什么嘛\n――稍微等一下啦！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1142
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e3e301cc:

    # "I half-jog to catch up to him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2362)
    "一路小跑地向那个背影追去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1147
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_795a6924:

    # "I'm searching for Kouya's secret.{p}Unaware of the details,\nI weave through the trees along with him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2371)
    "洸哉要找的那个秘密的东西。\n[漏れ]虽然不知道它的内容，\n还是和洸哉从树木的缝隙中穿过。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1148
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_1e41db4f:

    # "In my chest, I feel an excitement\nI haven't felt since I was a kid."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2375)
    "在胸中有着如同小孩子一般雀跃的兴奋感。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1149
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e980d665:

    # "We're on an adventure.\nWhen I think of it that way, it's very fun.\nIt feels like everything is eye-catching and fresh."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2376)
    "「冒险的旅程」。这样想着，就觉得无比地高兴。\n对眼前所见的东西全部都感到十分新鲜。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1150
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_373263ac:

    # "That's not the only thing I see.\nThe wind caresses me as it passes by,\nand smells of the trees and the grass at my feet."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2379)
    "不仅仅是能看见的东西。\n轻抚着[漏れ]吹过的风，脚下草木的气味。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1151
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_aaf776d5:

    # "The soft sunlight through the trees is warm."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2381)
    "以及透过叶间的温暖的阳光。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1152
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_75800adb:

    # "All of these things awaken\na simple pleasure within me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2383)
    "所有这些，都将[漏れ]心中那份已经忘记的\n简单的快乐唤醒。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1153
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d600a9ea:

    # fn "「...This reminds me, we used to walk\n like this when we did different things.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2386)
    fn "「……说起来，以前也像这样走到过各种各样的地方呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1154
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_21ae0a10:

    # "Without talking to anybody, I mutter that to myself.\nI reminisce about far away memories."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2389)
    "并没有想让谁听到，[漏れ]这样喃喃地说着。\n然后回想起来那些已经变得遥远的记忆。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1155
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f77b9854:

    # "All of them from the old times of Minasato."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2392)
    "从以前开始就什么都没有的水乡村。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1156
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_8b6ffbf9:

    # "The things we used to do as children,\nlike playing ball in the schoolyard,\ntalking about silly things in the candy store,"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2394)
    "说起小孩子的游戏，或是在学校操场踢足球啊，\n或是在糖果屋里一起说着傻话啊，"

# game/day 15.rpy:1157
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_529cbfe9:

    # "or adventuring around in the hills and fields."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2396)
    "又或者在周围的山丘上乱跑进行小小的冒险。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1158
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0ef6be66:

    # "That was the way things always were."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2398)
    "总是进行着那样的事。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1159
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0b955142:

    # "Of all those things, I think\n'adventure' has a special place in my heart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2400)
    "在那之中，[漏れ]感觉对那个「冒险」\n有着特别的感情。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1160
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_8460ed9e:

    # "We never did find anything outrageous.\nAn ordinary walk like this is adventure."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2403)
    "并不是想要发现什么重要的东西。\n而是如同散步一般的冒险。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1161
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3194c658:

    # "But just the act itself was something special."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2406)
    "但是，[漏れ]们的行为本身就是一种特别的东西，"

# game/day 15.rpy:1162
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_068fc170:

    # "Even if we found nothing, I was happy with that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2407)
    "即使什么都没有，只是那样就能感到很快乐了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1163
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3d55b038:

    # "To see things that have never been seen,\nthat's what I expected."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2409)
    "想看到没有见过的东西。\n那样子的期待，"

# game/day 15.rpy:1164
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_426094a9:

    # "There's definitely a world beyond\nus that we still don't know about, isn't there? \nThat was the wish I think was always in my heart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2412)
    "肯定在这前面有[漏れ]们所不知道的世界\n存在着。这样的愿望，\n一直在胸口萦绕着。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1165
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_846dfbe0:

    # "So I always enjoyed that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2416)
    "所以一直都很高兴。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1166
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4f86ccf6:

    # "Even five years later, that feeling has not changed."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2418)
    "而且，这种感觉直到5年后的今天也没有变化。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1167
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_02eb0ad3:

    # "Little by little, we've been growing into adults.\nEven though we've changed,\nthere are some things that have not."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2420)
    "身体渐渐长高的一点点长大的[漏れ]们。\n在那样的变化中，也还有不变的东西。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1168
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_def91746:

    # "Thinking about that seems to be a little exciting.\nI accidently laugh."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2423)
    "发现了这点的[漏れ]，觉得有点开心。\n笑声也自然地从嘴里漏了出来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1172
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_894035b8:

    # ka "「Hm, what is it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2429)
    ka "「嗯，怎么了？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1173
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_84d23a19:

    # "Hearing my laugh, Kouya turns to me, puzzled."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2432)
    "听到了[漏れ]的笑声，洸哉诧异地问道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1174
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_9a99b470:

    # fn "「Oh, just laughing while remembering... I guess?\n I used to walk around like this in Minasato.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2434)
    fn "「不，只是想到了一些好笑的事……吗？\n[漏れ]以前在水乡的时候也是这样走来走去的。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1175
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_de8038f1:

    # fn "「I used to do things like this for fun\n I was thinking about that and laughing」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2438)
    fn "「想起了那个时候也是这样快乐\n的心情呢，于是就笑出来了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1179
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_41fb3c03:

    # ka "「Returning to your childhood innocence?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2444)
    ka "「童心又回来了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1180
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_7a47808b:

    # fn "「You could say that. I'm glad\n I haven't forgotten this feeling.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2447)
    fn "「该怎么说呢，真高兴\n[漏れ]没有忘记[漏れ]所说的那种感觉啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1181
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0a1cd515:

    # fn "「Some parts of it are missing,\n but the time I spent with everybody five years ago\n is still perfectly within me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2451)
    fn "「虽然已经有很多地方脱落了，\n但是与大家一起经过的5年前的时光\n在好好地在[漏れ]的心中保存着啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1182
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_7d33ced6:

    # fn "「It would be great if I could\n remember everything, wouldn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2456)
    fn "「如果能够记住全部的东西就好了呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1183
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f0b802cc:

    # "I mock myself,\nand a bitter smile rises to my face."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2459)
    "说着稍微有点自嘲的话，\n苦涩的笑容浮现在[漏れ]的脸上。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1184
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_7ddc4108:

    # "It's fun to reminisce,\nI wonder why I haven't been\nable to remember these things until now?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2462)
    "明明记得是一间很快乐的事情，\n为什么却记不住其中的内容呢？"

# game/day 15.rpy:1185
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_1a62bc10:

    # "When I consider that, it's a little painful."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2465)
    "想到这点的话，就感到有点难过。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1189
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_9d090fe3:

    # ka "「What a lonesome thing to say.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2469)
    ka "「你在说什么寂寞的事啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1193
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e87b32a1:

    # "Kouya scoffs at me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2472)
    "但是[漏れ]说的那些，被洸哉反驳了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1194
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0ec844f8:

    # ka "「You can't help it if you forget about the past.\n Nobody is always living in the past.\n You can't know everything that has happened to you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2476)
    ka "「人会忘记以前的事那也是没办法的。\n谁也无法一直生活在过去里。\n所以自己之后会发生什么事也无法得知。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1195
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_cc9870dc:

    # ka "「However, [fn]-」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2482)
    ka "「但是呢[博行]――」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1199
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_97700dc7:

    # ka "「You should make memories now.\n You can't make up for what you lost,\n but you can have memories to fill in what you had.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2487)
    ka "「回忆从现在开始制造就好了。\n虽然已经失去的无法再找回来，\n你可以用拥有的回忆去填满它。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1200
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_aaa08a6b:

    # ka "「We should live in the present,\n shouldn't we?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2492)
    ka "「这不是很好吗。\n因为我们是『活在现在』啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1201
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_7c659639:

    # fn "「Kouya...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2496)
    fn "「洸哉……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1202
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ce669c22:

    # "His words are a little rough."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2499)
    "稍微有点粗暴的洸哉的话。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1203
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3f0b7a2b:

    # "But on the other side, I can see a certain kindness.\nI makes me feel happy.\nMy heart feels just a little lighter."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2501)
    "但是，从那之中却能感觉到他的温柔，\n[漏れ]十分高兴。\n心情有一点放松了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1204
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b11c63ce:

    # "Kouya isn't straightforward.\nI think that to myself, but don't say it.\nBut I always think about that when I'm around him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2505)
    "洸哉不是一个坦率的人。\n自己的想法，也不常常说出口。\n但是总是会考虑到周围的事。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1205
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_2c0209e4:

    # "I would say that his way of speaking\nwas also this soft back then,\nbut that was a long time ago."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2509)
    "这种说话的方式说穿了也是\n――当时还是用柔软的声音――从很久之前就开始了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1206
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b89edf29:

    # "That is definitely what I'm the most familiar with."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2512)
    "关于这一点[漏れ]们最清楚了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1207
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_275b94e7:

    # "So now I understand Kouya's consolation.\nTherefore, I'm happy."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2514)
    "所以现在[漏れ]明白了这是洸哉式的安慰。\n所以很高兴。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1211
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0b4afd4f:

    # ka "「Well, enjoy life now so that there's\n never a time when you hurt yourself.\n Just do that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2520)
    ka "「现在能够快乐地活下去的话，那就再好不过了。\n就是这样的。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1212
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_cd23abb5:

    # fn "「Yeah, you're right!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2524)
    fn "「――嗯，说得是呢！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1216
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_8ae5bb8a:

    # "It just as he says."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2530)
    "就像洸哉所说的那样。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1217
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f1044f0f:

    # "For now, I'll make lots of memories.\nIf I can remember how fun this was,\nthen I'll definitely be fine."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2532)
    "总之，现在制造出很多的回忆。\n并记住这种快乐的感觉的话，\n那样就一定没关系了吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1218
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_249f5f17:

    # "I think my heart is a little stronger.\nThen, Kouya and I begin to walk.\nThe grass and trees rustle as we pass by."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2536)
    "觉得心里稍微坚强了一点。\n然后又和洸哉一起开始迈着步伐。\n嘎吱嘎吱地踩着草木的小路前进。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1219
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4a85f2e4:

    # "There isn't much conversation,\nbut my time with Kouya is very comfortable."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2540)
    "虽然没有太多的对话，\n这样与洸哉在一起的时间感觉非常好。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1220
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_91f33bc1:

    # "I can't put it into words,\nbut it's like a strange sense of security."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2542)
    "那是一种难以用言语表达的，不可思议的安心感。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1221
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a9fcea41:

    # "I find myself breaking into a smile.\nThis really is fun.\nIt seems like I could walk like this forever."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2544)
    "通过自己脸上带着的笑容明白了。\n真的是，很快乐呢。\n感觉像是要这样一直地走下去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1222
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a003b00a:

    # "As if that feeling is made real,\nwe rapidly go deeper into the forest.\nWe still have not stopped walking."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2548)
    "仿佛是要将那样的心情变成现实一般，\n[漏れ]们不断地进入森林的深处。\n步子仍然没有停下来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1223
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_600dd7ff:

    # "I am enjoying this, but wait a minute?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2552)
    "很高兴。但是到底――"

# game/day 15.rpy:1224
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a9052979:

    # fn "「Now that I think of it...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2554)
    fn "「说起来啊，」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1225
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ba6d93ce:

    # "A question suddenly comes to mind,\nso I get Kouya's attention."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2557)
    "脑袋里突然产生了一个疑问，于是叫住了洸哉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1229
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4f77b663:

    # ka "「Hm?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2562)
    ka "「嗯？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1230
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_376cb6db:

    # "He looked over his shoulder at me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2565)
    "越过肩膀向这边看来，洸哉回答着。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1231
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_16a9b055:

    # fn "「What are you looking for, anyway?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2567)
    fn "「到底是要找什么东西呢？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1232
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_46e3a181:

    # "I ask the same question I asked before.\nI still haven't heard an answer."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2570)
    "之前提过的问题，再一次地被提出了。\n依旧没有得到答案。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1233
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_dfb497e7:

    # ka "「You still want to know?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2573)
    ka "「果然很想知道吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1234
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d031793a:

    # fn "「No, it's all right if you want to keep it a secret.\n But I think it would also be okay if you told me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2576)
    fn "「不，虽然你想保持秘密也行。\n不过我觉得你差不多也该告诉我了吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1235
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e7cd111f:

    # ka "「I see...\n Suffice to say, it's dark and wet,\n a damp place, I think.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2580)
    ka "「是呢……\n硬要说的话是该是暗暗的，湿湿的，\n潮潮的地方吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1236
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_cd0dee4f:

    # ka "「A cave would be best.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2585)
    ka "「有洞穴的话那最好了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1237
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_020566a4:

    # fn "「...Are you going there to\n get the legendary crystal?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2588)
    fn "「……你想要拿传说中的水晶吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1238
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ca5fb61f:

    # "I can do that for now if I can return."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2591)
    "总而言之先做个力所能及的回应吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1242
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_2c3c799f:

    # ka "「This isn't an RPG.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2596)
    ka "「那个是哪个RPG世界的故事啊？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1243
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_93eb25f7:

    # fn "「Mushroom hunting?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2599)
    fn "「那是蘑菇狩猎？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1244
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_21e633e2:

    # ka "「I might do that if they're growing there.\n Can you eat mushrooms that grow in caves?\n I don't think you can.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2602)
    ka "「如果那里有长的话也是可以啦……\n但是洞穴里生长的蘑菇能吃吗？\n我觉得那个不是能吃的样子。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1245
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f6db120a:

    # fn "「Yeah... I thought that, too.\n They're probably poisonous...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2607)
    fn "「唔……[漏れ]也这么认为。\n九成九会附加中毒的状态吧……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1246
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_1fa5aba6:

    # "It's not a crystal or mushrooms.\nWhat is it then?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2611)
    "总之既不是水晶也不是蘑菇。\n那么会是什么呢？"

# game/day 15.rpy:1250
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3996c32c:

    # ka "「Speaking of valuble, this might be valuable too...\n View looking around here as something fun to do.\n That way it will definitely be good.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2616)
    ka "「不是蘑菇很可惜啊，不过虽然很可惜……\n像那样把它当作寻找的乐趣就行了。\n那样的话就觉得不错了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1251
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ab62b304:

    # fn "「Hmm, if you say so.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2621)
    fn "「嗯，既然洸哉这么说了就这么办吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1257
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ef113668:

    # "We push our way further into the forest.{p}As our distance from the tent increases,\nthe rocks at our feet become noticeably more ragged."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2634)
    "更加地深入森林。\n已经远离了帐篷，\n脚下的岩石也变得明显起来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1258
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_48fdcc63:

    # "The tall grass from before is now short like moss,\nit's more like it's sticking to the rocks,\nrather than growing on them."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2638)
    "之前长得很高的草丛已经变成了短小的苔藓，\n与其说是生长在岩石中，不如说是附着在上面。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1262
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_55f1445d:

    # ka "「Stop for a second.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2644)
    ka "「先停一下。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1263
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_011cc30d:

    # "Kouya suddenly stands still."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2647)
    "走在前面的洸哉突然停下了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1264
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_477e0fef:

    # "Because it was so abrupt, the moss at my feet makes\nme slip and fall."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2649)
    "因为十分突然，脚踩在了青苔上差一点就\n要滑倒了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1265
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e55e8e55:

    # fn "「Ow... What is it, Kouya?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2652)
    fn "「哇……怎么了，洸哉？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1266
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b76de412:

    # "I ask him while using both\nhands to regain my posture."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2655)
    "挥动双手，总算调整好了平衡的[漏れ]问道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1267
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_815919b8:

    # ka "「...Can you hear that?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2657)
    ka "「……听到了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1268
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_de95c5cf:

    # fn "「Hear what?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2660)
    fn "「什么？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1269
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_6f1fcf36:

    # ka "「The sound of the wind.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2663)
    ka "「风的声音。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1270
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_78259099:

    # fn "「The wind...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2666)
    fn "「风……？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1275
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_70ec6cc6:

    # "He's right, the wind is blowing a little."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2672)
    "确实，稍微有一点风吹过来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1276
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3f330ebd:

    # "The breeze shakes the branches,\nand the leaves sound like bells."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2674)
    "风吹过树枝，\n树叶如同铃铛一般发出声音。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1277
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_143450ba:

    # "Hyuu-hyuu, sawa-sawa.\nIt's a very familiar sound."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2677)
    "咻咻～沙沙～\n是很好听的声音。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1278
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b3edc896:

    # fn "「I can certainly hear it, but...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2680)
    fn "「虽然是有听到……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1279
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_cba0b8cc:

    # ka "「That's not it. Keep listening.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2683)
    ka "「不是那个，再仔细地听。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1280
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3701d286:

    # fn "「A-all right...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2686)
    fn "「知、知道了……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1284
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4b3a9f38:

    # "I try listening harder."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2692)
    "于是侧着耳朵试着更仔细地听。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1285
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0a60fbc5:

    # "I just hear the wind from before.\nHyuu-hyuu, sawa-sawa."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2694)
    "从刚才就听到的风的声音。\n咻咻～沙沙～"

# game/day 15.rpy:1286
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_dee457da:

    # "But this is different. Kouya said so."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2697)
    "但是不是这个。洸哉这么说了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1287
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_7cc35f02:

    # "I close my eyes and concentrate harder."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2699)
    "闭上眼睛，让自己更加集中。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1288
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_47c55110:

    # "Hyuu-hyuu, sawa-sawa.\nI can hear many things being moved by the wind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2701)
    "咻咻～沙沙～\n风吹过各种各样的东西所发出的声音。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1289
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_6fc9d157:

    # fn "「...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2704)
    fn "「……？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1290
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b2fb5515:

    # "Before long,\nI notice some kind of low sound mixed in."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2707)
    "不久[漏れ]注意到了，\n有什么低沉的声音混杂在里面。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1294
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f92feaf2:

    # "It sounds like the low,\ndull groan of something inhaling."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2712)
    "有什么像吸入着什么，\n或者是低沉的呻吟一样的声音。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1295
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_16ff50c4:

    # fn "「It sounds like 'goooo', then 'buoooo'.{p} It's like the wind is being\n sucked in and blown out...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2715)
    fn "「能听到像是GU——然后是BO——一样的声音。\n像是，\n风被吸进去，然后再吹出来……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1299
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_616a3868:

    # ka "「You noticed it, good job.\n Now, let's go towards that sound.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2722)
    ka "「终于注意到了呢，干得不错。\n那么，朝那个声音的方向走吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1300
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_cce2ad10:

    # "Kouya pats me on the head,\nthen sets off again."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2726)
    "洸哉揉了揉[漏れ]的脑袋，然后再次开始前进。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1301
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_946e246e:

    # fn "「Oh, wait up, Kouya!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2728)
    fn "「啊，等一下啦洸哉。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1305
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_16056714:

    # "This time, to prevent slipping,\nI jump from rock to rock while following him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2734)
    "这次为了避免滑倒，[漏れ]在岩石间跳跃着追了上去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1310
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_fe4d1ad2:

    # "Then, we finally reach it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2743)
    "然后，[漏れ]们终于到达了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1311
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f63d79e0:

    # fn "「...It's a cave.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2745)
    fn "「……洞穴啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1312
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0dca0385:

    # "Actually, it seems too small to be called a cave.\nIt's more like a combination\nof big rocks, a little hole."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2748)
    "虽然那么说，不过要说是洞穴的话是有点小。\n那是个由大块的岩石所组成的小山洞而已。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1313
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4eadaf7f:

    # "The trees blocking the sunlight hide it.{p}It feels like it's a secret."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2751)
    "周围被高耸的树木环绕，\n隐藏在被遮蔽的阳光之外。\n给人一种秘密的感觉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1314
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a4421621:

    # fn "「Is this what you were looking for?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2755)
    fn "「要找的东西，就是这个？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1315
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_98883d8a:

    # "I ask him while pointing my\nindex finger at the dark entrance."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2758)
    "指着那黑暗的入口处，[漏れ]向洸哉问道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1319
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_8e68fd72:

    # ka "「I'm more interested in what's inside.{p} I want to do a little nature observation.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2763)
    ka "「里面有更多有趣的内容。\n我希望你能稍微做点自然观察。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1320
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_18836dfa:

    # fn "「Nature observation?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2767)
    fn "「自然观察？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1321
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_1d194dae:

    # ka "「Well, you'll see when we go in.{p} I'll go first, you follow me slowly.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2770)
    ka "「那个，你进去以后就明白了。\n我在前面带路，慢慢地跟着我吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1322
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_5c3f1ab0:

    # "After saying that,\nKouya suddenly grabs my right hand."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2774)
    "这么说着，洸哉突然抓住[漏れ]的右手。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1323
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_53df0d70:

    # fn "「Wha-{w=.2}Kouya...!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2776)
    fn "「等下，洸哉……！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1324
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_2fdd25e2:

    # ka "「Hm? What?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2779)
    ka "「嗯，怎么了？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1325
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_05c31b6c:

    # fn "「N-nothing...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2782)
    fn "「没、没什么啦……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1326
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4464ce71:

    # "When he unexpectedly grabbed my hand,\nI yelled out in surprise.{p}I couldn't help it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2785)
    "突然被握住手的[漏れ]，吓得一下子就发出了声。\n实在是没有忍住。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1327
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_209b82b4:

    # "Kouya gives me a slightly quizzical look,\nbut then keeps pulling on my hand."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2788)
    "洸哉对[漏れ]的态度\n做出了一个不可思议的表情，\n不过马上牵着[漏れ]的手开始走了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1328
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d5e6dadb:

    # "Both of us enter the cave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2792)
    "两个人，进入山洞。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1334
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_86ca4ccf:

    # "Soon, damp air wraps around my body.{p}It feels kind of weird."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2796)
    "潮湿的空气一瞬间就把肌肤缠绕住了。\n稍微有点不舒服。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1335
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_58297d3d:

    # "As you can imagine from being in the dark,\nI can only see a little from\nthe light coming in from outside."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2799)
    "山洞里就如想象中一般的黑暗，\n几乎没有外面的光线照射进来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1336
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_60d2e1fc:

    # "In the all-too-faint light,\nI have no idea how far this hole goes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2802)
    "借着微弱的光线，\n也不知道这个山洞最后延伸到哪里。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1337
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ffee949a:

    # fn "「Kouya, it's so dark that\n I can't see a thing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2805)
    fn "「洸哉，这么暗的话果然什么都看不到啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1338
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a212f117:

    # ka "「Hold on, I'll get some light」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2808)
    ka "「稍等一下，现在就弄个亮。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1344
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_38b33e0c:

    # "After I hear a scraping sound a few times,\na dim light illuminates around us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2813)
    "几次摩擦的声音过后，周围被昏暗的光线照亮了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1345
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4ee6be66:

    # "I can't see it because it's in my blind spot,\nbut it seems Kouya is using a lighter."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2814)
    "[漏れ]虽然站在死角看得不是很清楚，\n不过看起来是洸哉打亮了一个打火机的样子。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1346
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_aa435b9f:

    # fn "「Huh? You smoke?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2817)
    fn "「诶，洸哉有在吸烟吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1350
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b0a5f1b8:

    # ka "「No,{w} just because I have a lighter\n doesn't mean I smoke.{p} It's a handy thing to have if you're camping.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2822)
    ka "「没有吸烟啦。不要看到拿着打火机的\n就把它和吸烟联系在一起。\n来野营的话，准备打火机总会派上用场的吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1351
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d090c9a3:

    # fn "「Oh, I see...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2828)
    fn "「啊原来如此……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1352
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b49fcbed:

    # ka "「Come on, let's go.{p} If we take too long, Tatsuki-san will yell at us.{p} Watch your step.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2831)
    ka "「那走吧。\n再这么慢悠悠的话，可是会被辰树骂的。\n当心脚下。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1356
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e4d8893f:

    # "Saying that, Kouya moves on,{p}still gripping my hand."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2839)
    "这么说着，洸哉继续前进。\n依然抓着[漏れ]的手。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1357
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_bd644306:

    # "I suddenly feel my temperature rise,\nand my heart beats faster.{p}My face is probably turning red."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2842)
    "突然对那个温度有点在意，心跳也加速了。\n[漏れ]现在的脸一定是红透了吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1358
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_529967ca:

    # "Somewhat embarrassed, I bend my head\nand look down a little."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2845)
    "不知道为什么觉得有点害羞，[漏れ]稍微低下头\n望着地面。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1362
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_08af084a:

    # ka "「Stop.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2851)
    ka "「停下。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1363
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_2741fc82:

    # fn "「Alri-{w=.2}oof!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2854)
    fn "「哇啊噢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1367
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a7f5aca4:

    # "Once again, Kouya suddenly tells me to stop."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2860)
    "又是突然出现的洸哉的停止命令。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1368
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_35c4f5de:

    # "This time, instead of losing my balance,\nI decide to headbutt Kouya's back."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2862)
    "这次作为滑倒的代替，\n[漏れ]决定用头撞向洸哉的后背。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1369
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_cfbe0552:

    # "I think it's a cliched thing for me to do."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2865)
    "「多么俗套的事啊」[漏れ]这么想着。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1370
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_11e63288:

    # ka "「What's with the headbutt...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2867)
    ka "「干嘛用头撞……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1371
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_c92f5ee2:

    # fn "「Sorry...\n But could you say 'stop' a little bit\n earlier than when you actually do stop?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2870)
    fn "「对不起……\n但是你能在停止之前稍微早一点说吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1375
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d68af471:

    # ka "「...All right. Good news.{p} It looks like our target is here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2877)
    ka "「……嗯算了，告诉你一个好消息。\n这里看起来就是我们的目的地了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1379
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_28a8f42d:

    # "Suddenly, the light around us disappears.{p}Once again, our surroundings are pitch-black."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2888)
    "突然，照亮周围的光消失了。\n再一次地被黑暗填满。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1380
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f69f4f72:

    # "I can't even see Kouya's satisfied\nappearance in front of me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2890)
    "就在眼前的洸哉的身体，也完全看不到。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1381
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_5372d855:

    # fn "「Kouya?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2892)
    fn "「洸哉？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1382
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_34c6753d:

    # ka "「Watch.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2895)
    ka "「嗯，看着。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1383
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e51ea9b4:

    # "When he says that, I can't say anything more.\nWhile he talks to me,\nI stare into the darkness."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2898)
    "既然都这么说了，[漏れ]也没有什么别的好说的。\n于是按照洸哉的话，\n盯着什么都看不到的黑暗。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1388
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_c3566670:

    # "Then, an optical illusion?\nIt looks like the walls of the\ncave are starting to gradually light up."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2905)
    "是眼睛的错觉吗？\n洞穴的墙壁好像渐渐地亮了起来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1389
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0bd5ea6e:

    # fn "「Huh...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2908)
    fn "「唔……？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1390
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3ba2e19b:

    # "But the illusion is real,\nthe light keeps getting brighter."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2911)
    "但是那错觉是现实，光线变得更加亮了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1398
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f4979512:

    # "Soon, I can see it clearly.\nIt changes to the color of young green leaves,\nwith a hint of gold."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2922)
    "不久[漏れ]的眼前已经很清晰了，\n嫩叶的绿色，除此之外稍微带着一点金色的光辉映了出来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1399
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_03d979bc:

    # "It's a weak light, like fireflies,\nbut it's definitely there.\nA quiet glittering fills this narrow space."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2925)
    "虽然是像萤火虫一样微弱的光，\n确实在那里存在着，\n像要将这个狭窄空间填满一般静静地闪耀着。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1400
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_01b6eab8:

    # "There are spots where the\nlight is stronger than others,\nand makes it look like some kind of pattern."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2929)
    "有光强的地方，也有稍微弱一些的地方，\n那个强弱看起来组成了什么图案一般。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1401
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ea5cecb4:

    # "It's beautiful.{p}It looks as if it's been embedded\nwith stars from the night sky."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2932)
    "真漂亮啊。\n将夜空的星星镶嵌在一面的话，\n大概就是这个样子吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1402
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_e355a958:

    # "It seems magical, mysterious, and beautiful.{p}A gasp of wonder escapes from my mouth."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2936)
    "这样的幻想、神秘、美丽。\n感叹的声音不由自主地从口中吐露出来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1406
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_8afc5cc6:

    # fn "「Wow...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2942)
    fn "「哇……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1407
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a2335a0b:

    # ka "「Can you see it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2945)
    ka "「看到了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1408
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_3cc718b5:

    # fn "「Yeah... It's like the walls are shining...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2948)
    fn "「嗯……好像，墙壁在发光一样……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1409
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d121305d:

    # ka "「It's luminous moss.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2951)
    ka "「光藓。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1410
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_0bd5ea6e_1:

    # fn "「Huh...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2955)
    fn "「诶……？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1411
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_82091d54:

    # "I was so fascinated by the light\nthat I didn't quite understand what Kouya said."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2957)
    "看着光入迷了，\n完全没有理解洸哉说的话。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1412
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b7167598:

    # "I think he said... Luminous moss."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2959)
    "光藓……是什么呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1413
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_53f097d5:

    # ka "「This light is true to the moss' name.{p} It absorbs the small amount of light in here,\n which is why it appears to be shining.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2962)
    ka "「这些光呢，是那个名字的苔藓的真面目。\n将入口进入的少量的光反射，\n这样就能看到那样的光。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1414
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_baa7f94d:

    # ka "「You might find it in other places,\nbut it usually grows in damp places,\nespecially on rocks and in caves like this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2967)
    ka "「虽然也能在别的地方找到苔藓，\n在潮湿的地方――特别是在岩石的背阴面\n或者洞窟里生长的比较多。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1415
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_73a74f37:

    # ka "「It's not very hardy,\n so a small change in its environment\n can instantly kill it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2972)
    ka "「因为没有那么强大的生命力，\n稍微一点环境的变化就会致死了，\n已经濒临灭绝的危机了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1416
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_8bf1790b:

    # ka "「It's on the verge of extinction.\n Because of that, it's a protected species,\n so you can't take it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2977)
    ka "「顺便说一下这个是自然保护植物。[wdt]你不可以带走。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1417
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_9f621ea4:

    # fn "「Wow...{w=.2} That was very detailed, Kouya.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2980)
    fn "「诶……洸哉知道得很清楚呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1418
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_c97f520d:

    # ka "「I just know about this.{p} I learned about it a long time ago... From my dad.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2983)
    ka "「只有这个啊。\n以前有人教过我……我父亲。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1419
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_898adf90:

    # fn "「Really?{p} So you and your dad have been here before?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2987)
    fn "「真的吗？\n那么，到这里也是那时候和大叔？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1420
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_d2232c22:

    # ka "「No, this is my first time here.{p} I couldn't sleep last night, so I wandered around,\n and saw this on a rock near the tent.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2991)
    ka "「不，这里是今天第一次来。\n昨天夜里睡不着出来乱逛，\n在一个靠近帐篷的岩石上看到了这家伙。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1421
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_22c3bd05:

    # ka "「The area around here is practically untouched,\n it's like it's all that remains of nature.\n I think this might be what I'm looking for.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 2996)
    ka "「因为这一带几乎没有被开发，\n还残留着自然的样子。[l]\n我想是不是会有那个呢，于是就找了一下。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1422
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_686bc52c:

    # ka "「That's good, this wasn't a wasted trip.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3001)
    ka "「太好了呢，没有白费一番工夫。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1426
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_f88b96f3:

    # ka "「I even got to show this to you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3007)
    ka "「――想让你，也看一下这些。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1427
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_b8a0447c:

    # "In the dim green light, I can see Kouya smiling.{p}That smile makes me happy for some reason."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3010)
    "在绿色的光照出的明亮中，可以看见微笑着的洸哉的身姿。\n那个笑容，让[漏れ]感觉到很高兴。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1428
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_7c659639_1:

    # fn "「Kouya...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3014)
    fn "「洸哉……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1429
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_5aaa1e46:

    # ka "「Are you glad you went?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3016)
    ka "「来这里高兴吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1430
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_55dc3168:

    # fn "「Yes, Thank you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3019)
    fn "「――嗯，谢谢你。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1431
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_66549f15:

    # "For a while after that, we silently\ngaze at the light in the cave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3022)
    "在那之后一段时间，[漏れ]们都只是望着\n洞穴一言不发。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1432
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_a1129abd:

    # "There's nothing you can do about forgotten memories.{p}I'll be all right if I can remember the fun times.{p}That's what I thought earlier."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3025)
    "没有能够让记忆不忘记的方法是没办法的事。\n只要记住快乐的事那就好了。\n刚才是这么认为的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1433
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_ebf2f31e:

    # "But, no matter what,\nI will not forget this."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3029)
    "但是，\n\n――只有这个景色，无论\n怎么样都不想要忘记。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1434
translate chinese_simplified camp15_kouya_4611d1ea:

    # "That alone is what I wish for."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3034)
    "只有这个，是[漏れ]强烈的愿望。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1442
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b7c453da:

    # "...{p}A number of days have passed since that event,{w=.2}\nBut Juuichi-san still isn't speaking to me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3052,3053,3054)
    "……[l]\n在那之后已经过了好几天，[wdt]\n但[漏れ]和柔一之间还是很尴尬。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1443
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_79e9d1c6:

    # "...I'd better choose someone else to hang out with."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3056)
    "还是暂时不要去找柔一好了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1451
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_d7dfaf03:

    # fn "「What are you going to do, Juuichi-san?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3065,3066)
    fn "【博行】\n「柔一打算做什么呢？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1452
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_e9085180:

    # "I ask Juuichi-san, who has his arms crossed,\ndeep in thought."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3068)
    "[漏れ]向两手抱胸在思考着的柔一问道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1457
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_33d57385:

    # ju "「Hmm...{p} Takahara said there are hot springs nearby.{p} Perhaps they will take care of my fatigue.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3074,3075,3076,3077)
    ju "【柔一】\n「这个嘛……[l]\n高原也有提过，[wdt]这附近好像有温泉的样子。[l]\n去泡泡温泉来消除这几天的疲劳似乎也不错。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1458
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_2867f7f5:

    # "That's right,{w=.2} he trains hard every day.{p}He doesn't talk about it,{w=.2}\nbut you can see the fatigue in his eyes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3079,3080,3081)
    "对喔，[wdt]柔一每天都在进行很辛苦的练习。[l]\n虽然从外表上看不太出来，[wdt]\n但其实已经积累了相当大量的疲劳也不一定。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1459
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_80128e63:

    # "All right, I too will help\nease Juuichi-san's fatigue!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3083,3084)
    "好，[wdt][漏れ]为了治愈柔一的疲劳，\n[漏れ]也来尽力帮忙吧！"

# game/day 15.rpy:1460
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4e3a73f3:

    # "...My ulterior motive for doing\nthis is to see him naked?\nUhh... No! Not at all!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3086,3087,3088)
    "【博行】\n「[漏れ]也可以一起去吗？[l]\n请让[漏れ]帮你刷背什么的吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1461
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_8eeac9e4:

    # fn "「Is it all right if I come with you?{p} I can wash your back, if you like.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3086-3088)
    fn "「[漏れ]也可以一起去吗？[l]请让[漏れ]帮你刷背什么的吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1465
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4e2d3fde:

    # ju "「I don't mind...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3095,3096)
    ju "这时柔一看向了辰兄那里。[l]\n跟着看过去，[wdt]只看到辰兄正在和虎彦一起热烈地讨论着。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1466
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_38f6cc03:

    # "Juuichi-san glances over at Tatsu-nii.{p}From here, I can see him making a fuss with Torahiko\nabout something."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3098,3099)
    "听他们对话的内容，[wdt]似乎辰兄他们\n打算要去探险的样子。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1467
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_54a1cf9e:

    # "...Apparently, Tatsu-nii is heading out to explore."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3103,3104,3105)
    "【柔一】\n「和辰他们一起去的话，[wdt]\n肯定会比较有趣吧？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1471
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_6015602e:

    # ju "「You don't think Tatsu-san\n is doing something more interesting?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3103-3105)
    ju "「和辰他们一起去的话，[l]肯定会比较有趣吧？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1472
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_266a0df9:

    # fn "「No,{w=.2} I'd like to come with you.\n Hot springs are hard to find in the city...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3111,3112,3113)
    fn "听他们的说法，[wdt]好像要越过几千座山，\n以找到龙神出现的神秘泉水为目标的样子。[l]\n……辰兄他们，[wdt]应该可以平安回来吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1473
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_916d024b:

    # "The others are talking of a quest\nto find the fountain of mystery.\n...Tatsu-nii, I hope you come back in one piece."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3115,3116)
    "不知道是不是[漏れ]的心声传达过去了，[wdt]\n柔一浅浅地叹了口气。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1474
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_16635b32:

    # "Juuichi-san looks like he's about to say something,\nthen sighs."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3120,3121,3122)
    "【柔一】\n「……唉，[wdt]的确这次可能是\n[西村]的选择比较明智。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1478
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_c97349a9:

    # ju "「...Well, you might be choosing wisely this time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3120-3122)
    ju "「……唉，[wdt]的确这次可能是[西村]的选择比较明智。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1479
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_cf766115:

    # fn "「Should we get going,\n before we get involved with Tatsu-nii?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3124,3125)
    fn "【博行】\n「那，[wdt]在被辰兄抓过去之前快走吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1483
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_40f2a2a4:

    # ju "「Yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3130,3131)
    ju "【柔一】\n「啊啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1487
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_32b4a55d:

    # "Sneaking back to the tent,{w=.2}\nwe grab our towels."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3138,3139)
    "然后，[wdt]就趁着辰兄他们正在争论到底要由谁来当\n探险队长而没注意的时候，[wdt]蹑手蹑脚地从旁边走了过去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1488
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_80095e73:

    # "There's a dispute over who will lead the expedition.\nWe tiptoe past so Tatsu-nii doesn't notice us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3144,3145)
    "【深】\n「……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1492
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_bef95801:

    # si "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3147,3148)
    si "啊。[l]\n不小心和深四目交接了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1493
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_8ccf2273:

    # "Oh.{p}Shin-kun's eyes meet mine."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3150,3151)
    "[漏れ]伸手在面前合什，[wdt]低头向深君做出拜托的动作。[l]\n抱歉，[wdt]请当作没看到[漏れ]吧！"

# game/day 15.rpy:1494
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4653f7a1:

    # "I put my hands together in front of my face and bow.{p}Sorry, please overlook this."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3150)
    "[漏れ]伸手在面前合什，[wdt]低头向深君做出拜托的动作。[l]抱歉，[wdt]请当作没看到[漏れ]吧！"

# game/day 15.rpy:1498
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_5a7a2cda:

    # "Shin-kun sighs and shrugs.{p}It seems he's pretending not to see us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3161,3162)
    "谢谢你，深君！[l]\n回到村子里后得想办法跟他道谢才行。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1502
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_24b3f408:

    # "Thank you, Shin-kun!{p}I'll have to show my gratitude somehow,\nwhen we get back to the village."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3164,3165)
    "就这样，[wdt][漏れ]和柔一便朝向露营场\n附近的温泉出发了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1503
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b9b90d92:

    # "Juuichi-san and I depart from the campsite,\nheading towards the hot springs."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3181,3182)
    "【柔一】\n「这是这里了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1513
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_e29b13f0:

    # ju "「We're here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3181)
    ju "「这是这里了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1514
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_3d0a3218:

    # "After a 15 minute walk from the tents,\nwe finally arrive at our destination."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3187,3188,3189)
    "……哎，这路还真的是很难走啊。[l]\n一下上坡一下下坡，[wdt]在几乎没有道路的地方前进……该怎么说，[wdt]\n感觉好像在爬山似的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1515
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_3294beaa:

    # "...Haah, that journey was pretty painful.{p}We went up and down slopes, on a trackless path...{w=.2}\nIt felt a bit like climbing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3187)
    "……哎，这路还真的是很难走啊。[l]一下上坡一下下坡，[wdt]在几乎没有道路的地方前进……该怎么说，[wdt]感觉好像在爬山似的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1516
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b54f105a:

    # "Is he used to walking in the mountains,\nor is his physical strength just that good?{p}His breathing hasn't changed at all."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3194,3195)
    "相比之下，[wdt]平常几乎没有在做运动，\n就走这种山路[漏れ]却已经快累瘫了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1517
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_a5df2e5d:

    # "On the other hand,{w=.2} I don't play sports.\nI was exhausted before we even got here."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3194)
    "相比之下，[wdt]平常几乎没有在做运动，[l]就走这种山路[漏れ]却已经快累瘫了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1518
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_c1034ff1:

    # "...Ooh,{w=.2} if I collapse before I soothe Juuichi-san,\nit'll be like putting the horse before the cart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3200,3201,3202)
    "哎，不过既然已经到目的地了，[wdt]\n剩下的也就只有跳进温泉里了！[l]\n这样这段路上的疲劳也会消散了吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1519
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_8e17e33e:

    # "Well, we're already here,{w=.2}\nso let's get in the hot spring!{p}That should blow away my fatigue."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3204,3205)
    "[漏れ]开始东张西望了起来。[l]\n咦，[wdt]温泉在哪里啊。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1520
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_6303ce15:

    # "I look around.{p}Umm,{w=.2} where is this hot spring?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3207,3208,3209)
    "眼前的小溪正演奏着能治愈人心的乐声。[l]\n因为是比较上游的地方，[wdt]\n河里四处散落着拳头大的石头。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1521
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_3feb65fd:

    # "In front of me, a stream is making a soothing sound.{p}Scattered further upstream are\nrocks about the size of a fist."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3207)
    "眼前的小溪正演奏着能治愈人心的乐声。[l]因为是比较上游的地方，[wdt]河里四处散落着拳头大的石头。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1522
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_488aee8f:

    # "The water is very clear.{p}It looks good enough to drink."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3214,3215)
    "看着在日光照射下反射着灿烂的的光芒的水面，[wdt]\n[漏れ]不禁眯起了眼。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1523
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_7002305a:

    # "The sunlight reflecting off the surface\nshines like a kaleidoscope,\nand I have to squint my eyes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3217,3218)
    "四处看去都是美丽的自然景观。[l]\n……嗯，这样是很好。[wdt]虽然是很好啦。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1524
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_43ecea0e:

    # "There's nature as far as the eye can see.{p}...It's really nice here."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3220,3221)
    "可是，温泉设施呢？[l]\n和柔一一起度过的休闲时光呢？"

# game/day 15.rpy:1525
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_ebc3d200:

    # "Wait, this is the hot spring?{p}This is where I'm relaxing with Juuichi-san?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3223,3224)
    "【柔一】\n「没有那种东西。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1526
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_73c31316:

    # ju "「That's not it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3233-3234)
    ju "「不是说这里有温泉冒出来吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1530
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4504a52f:

    # fn "「Huh?!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3231)
    fn "柔一说的话让[漏れ]不假思索地大喊了出来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1531
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_7d07e397:

    # "I cry out in surprise at his words."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3233,3234)
    "【博行】\n「不是说这里有温泉冒出来吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1532
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_153e9244:

    # fn "「There isn't a hot spring here?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3233-3234)
    fn "「不是说这里有温泉冒出来吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1533
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_d2fbd627:

    # ju "「There is.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3243)
    ju "柔一说完后，[wdt]向河边快步走去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1538
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_bd9a2266:

    # "Saying that, Juuichi-san walks\nbriskly towards the stream."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3245,3246)
    "是怎么回事啊。[l]\n完全没有看到哪里有温泉冒出来啊……"

# game/day 15.rpy:1539
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_5ba9ffb8:

    # "What does he mean?{p}There's a hot spring here, but I can't see it...?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3248,3249,3250)
    "柔一像是在找什么掉了的东西的样子一直往下看着。[l]\n不知道是不是终于发现了目标物，[wdt]\n他转身向[漏れ]这里招了招手。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1540
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_446b42f2:

    # "Juuichi-san searches around for something.{p}Before long, he finds it.{w=.2} Looking towards me,\nhe beckons me over."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3248)
    "柔一像是在找什么掉了的东西的样子一直往下看着。[l]不知道是不是终于发现了目标物，[wdt]他转身向[漏れ]这里招了招手。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1541
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_77481729:

    # "Still uncertain, I walk over to where he's standing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3252)
    "[漏れ]带着半信半疑的心情，[wdt]走到了柔一的身旁。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1545
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4a1c24d3:

    # ju "「Try feeling the water here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3258)
    ju "「你摸摸看这里的水。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1546
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4ddfa11b:

    # "I lean down, and dip my hand into the stream...{w=.2}\n{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3260)
    "[漏れ]照他所说的蹲了下来，[wdt][se mizu07]把手放到眼前的河流中。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1548
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_e05e145f:

    # extend "Huh? It feels strange. I look up at Juuichi-san."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3266,3267)
    extend "【博行】\n「这个水，[wdt]感觉温温的……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1549
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_61602f87:

    # fn "「This water is warm...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3274-3276)
    fn "柔一听到[漏れ]说的话后点了点头。[l]虽然因为河水流过而变得稀薄了，[wdt]但这里似乎有温泉流出来的样子。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1553
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_ad633e01:

    # ju "「It is.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3274,3275,3276)
    ju "柔一听到[漏れ]说的话后点了点头。[l]\n虽然因为河水流过而变得稀薄了，[wdt]\n但这里似乎有温泉流出来的样子。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1554
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_e92307b7:

    # "He nods his head in confirmation."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3278,3279)
    "确实仔细一看的话，[wdt]可以发现水面上有着\n许多小小的气泡不断浮上来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1555
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b775803f:

    # "When I look closely,\nI can see small bubbles rising to the surface."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3278)
    "确实仔细一看的话，[wdt]可以发现水面上有着许多小小的气泡不断浮上来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1556
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_cb1d863e:

    # fn "「...Even though there is a hot spring here,\n how are we going to soak in this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3282)
    fn "「……咦，[wdt]可是就算有温泉，没有池子的话，还是不能泡不是吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1557
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_fd5de0e0:

    # "Confused, I ask Juuichi-san my question."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3285)
    "[漏れ]向柔一提出了这个理所当然的疑问。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1561
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_514741a8:

    # ju "「That's what this is for.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3290)
    ju "「就是因此，[wdt]才带了这个。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1567
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_21618fd9:

    # "Juuichi-san thrusts a shovel into the ground.\n...I have been wondering why he brought a shovel."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3294)
    "柔一把铲子插到了地上。[l]……之前就一直觉得奇怪，为什么泡温泉要带铲子的说。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1568
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_79c7a148:

    # fn "「...I'm guessing that's for making our own bath?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3299)
    fn "「……该不会，要用这个自己动手挖出池子来吧？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1569
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_0bcde583:

    # ju "「That is correct.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3302)
    ju "「就是这样。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1570
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_88d91c3d:

    # "Once again, Juuichi-san nods approvingly.{p}...I see, we still have some work to do before\nwe can relax in the hot spring."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3304)
    "柔一用力地点了点头。[l]……是吗，在可以泡温泉之前还有些工作不得不做吗。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1571
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_7a91247f:

    # "I'm already exhausted from our walk,{w=.2}\nand I feel dizzy."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3311,3312)
    "……不过，[wdt]这些都是为了柔一。[l]\n加油啊，[漏れ]！[wdt]　奋斗吧！"

# game/day 15.rpy:1572
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_699a74fd:

    # "...But I'm doing this all for Juuichi-san.{p}I'll do my best!{w=.2} Go me!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3314,3315,3316)
    "【柔一】\n「那，开始吧。[wdt]我来挖洞。[l]\n[西村]则负责把挖的洞整理成适合泡温泉的样子。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1573
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_2ba8e02f:

    # ju "「Now, let's begin.{w=.2} I'll dig the hole.{p} You shape it so that it's easy to get into.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3315)
    ju "「那，开始吧。[wdt]我来挖洞。[l][西村]则负责把挖的洞整理成适合泡温泉的样子。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1574
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_669445d4:

    # fn "「Got it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3324,3325)
    fn "于是[漏れ]们便开始了手工制作温泉的工作。[l]\n首先，要将比较大块的石头给搬到旁边去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1578
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_09ecedb2:

    # "We start contructing our handmade spa.{p}First, we move the stones that are too big."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3327,3328,3329)
    "就在[漏れ]努力将一块石头抱起来，\n用力到脸都红了的时候，[wdt]旁边的柔一却\n一手夹着一颗同样大的石头直接走了过去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1579
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_8f76c79e:

    # "Carrying them makes my face red with effort.{w=.2}\nNext to me, Juuichi-san carries two of similar size."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3331,3332,3333)
    "……[漏れ]用两只手拼了命才能抬起来的，[wdt]\n柔一却用一只手就可以轻松搬运了。[l]而且，还是一次两颗。[l]\n……[漏れ]，[wdt]是不是也该稍微锻炼一下身体比较好呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1580
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_305f7ab7:

    # "...Even though I'm working hard with both hands,{w=.2}\nhe easily carries it in one.{p}Plus, he's doing two at a time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3335,3336)
    "在大块的石头差不多都搬完之后，[wdt]就开始用铲子将较小的砾石\n给挖走的工作了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1581
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_1511c026:

    # "...Maybe I should train my body a bit more."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3338,3339,3340)
    "柔一在挖土的时候，[wdt][漏れ]也只能在旁边\n看着他的动作给他加油打气。[l]\n加油啊柔一，[wdt]很快就要可以泡温泉了！"

# game/day 15.rpy:1582
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_58d8f3d7:

    # "We get most of the big stones out of the way,{w=.2}\nthen get to work with the shovel."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3342,3343)
    "在柔一挖到差不多[漏れ]小腿深的时候，[wdt]\n终于在石头的缝隙间流出了温泉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1583
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_053e0ea0:

    # "While working with Juuichi-san,{w=.2}\nI can only really offer my support.{p}Hang in there, Juuichi-san, our goal is in sight!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3345,3346)
    "【柔一】\n「……唔。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1584
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_961ff49d:

    # "He digs until the hole is about as deep as my leg.{w=.2}\nBefore long, the hot spring gushes\nout from between the rocks."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3343)
    "在柔一挖到差不多[漏れ]小腿深的时候，[wdt]终于在石头的缝隙间流出了温泉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1585
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_9dcf7c45:

    # ju "「...Hmm.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3342-3343)
    ju "在柔一挖到差不多[漏れ]小腿深的时候，[wdt]终于在石头的缝隙间流出了温泉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1586
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_877a9bd9:

    # "Juuichi-san quickly gets out of the hole."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3356,3357)
    "【柔一】\n「啊不，[wdt]比想象中还要烫所以吓了一跳。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1587
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_fb2a4874:

    # fn "「Is something wrong,{w=.2} Juuichi-san?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3359,3360,3361)
    fn "啊，是这样啊。[l]\n刚刚的温泉因为河水的关系而变成只是微温，[wdt]\n但现在刚挖出的是源泉所以比较烫吗。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1591
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_1a6d42da:

    # ju "「No,{w=.2} it's just hotter than I thought it would be.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3366,3367,3368)
    ju "[漏れ]把铲子借了过来，[wdt]\n在河水和洞穴间挖出了一条连通的水道。[l]\n冷水开始慢慢地流到了高温的温泉中。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1592
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_cc5ff464:

    # "Oh, really?{p}The water mixed with the stream was warm earlier,{w=.2}\nbut it looks like we're getting to the source."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3370,3371,3372)
    "柔一低声地说了声原来如此。[l]\n听起来语气中似乎有夸奖的意思，[wdt]\n让[漏れ]忍不住高兴了一下。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1596
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_1c90a546:

    # "I borrow the shovel from him,{w=.2}\nand make a canal linking the river to our bath.{p}Cold water begins trickling in to our hot spring."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3374,3375,3376)
    "几分钟后，[wdt]柔一挖出来的洞中已经流满了水。[l]\n[漏れ]弄了个小小的堤防把水道挡了起来。[l]如果又变热的话，[wdt]\n只要把这个弄倒让水流进来就没问题了……[wdt]大概。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1597
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_784992a2:

    # "Juuichi-san nods again, approvingly.{p}That felt like a compliment.{w=.2}\nIt makes me happy."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3378,3379)
    "[漏れ]把洞穴底部给挖平，[wdt]在旁边用大块的石头\n圈了起来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1598
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_6ddc6c11:

    # "A few minutes later, the hole is full of water.{p}We make a levee to block the small canal.{w=.2}\nWhen it gets too hot, we can just add more cold in."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3381,3382,3383)
    "把手放进水中试了一下温度。[l]\n要说温泉的话温度稍微有点低啦，[wdt]\n不过现在是夏天这种温度应该刚刚好吧？"

# game/day 15.rpy:1599
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_c81de57d:

    # "I flatten the bottom of the hole,\nand surround the edge with rocks."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3385,3386,3387)
    "……嗯，[wdt]这样应该可以。[l]\n[漏れ]向旁边看着[漏れ]工作的柔一\n露出笑脸说道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1600
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4406544b:

    # "I check the temperature with my hand.{p}It might be a little cool,{w=.2}\nbut it's summer, so I think this is good."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3389,3390)
    "【博行】\n「完成了呢！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1601
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_7892d2e2:

    # "...Then again, maybe not.{p}I talk to Juuichi-san, who is watching me work\nwith a small smile on his face."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3395,3396)
    "【柔一】\n「啊啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1602
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_c4809404:

    # fn "「It's done!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3389)
    fn "「完成了呢！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1606
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_40f2a2a4_1:

    # ju "「Yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3394,3395)
    ju "【柔一】\n「啊啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1607
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_231de6b3:

    # "At first, I thought I was going to hate this.\nBut somehow, making this\nopen-air bath was really absorbing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3402,3403)
    "【博行】\n「快快，[wdt]进去泡吧进去泡吧！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1608
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_89bb757e:

    # fn "「All right, let's get in!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3407,3408,3409)
    fn "[漏れ]满怀期待地把衣服跟裤子\n脱了下来。[l]脱到只剩内裤的时候，[wdt]\n[漏れ]突然注意到柔一完全没有开始脱衣服。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1612
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b200ad79:

    # "Full of anticipation, I pull off my shirt and pants.\nStanding there in my underwear,{w=.2}\nI see Juuichi-san isn't taking his clothes off."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3411,3412)
    "【博行】\n「柔一，[wdt]怎么了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1613
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_1b46d274:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san,{w=.2} what's wrong?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3417-3418)
    fn "「……没有，[wdt]只是觉得两个人进去好像有点挤。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1617
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_7998d267:

    # ju "「...This bath might be a too small for two people.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3420,3421,3422)
    ju "柔一这么一说，[wdt][漏れ]转头看了看刚做好的露天温泉。[l]\n……确实，只有一个人进去的话还算蛮宽的，[wdt]\n不过和柔一一起进去的话可能就有点太挤了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1618
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_bdfee0e9:

    # "As he says that, I take a look at it.{p}...He's right. There might be enough room for me,{w=.2}\nbut it might be a little difficult for both of us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3424,3425)
    "糟糕。[l]\n没想到，[wdt]竟然会犯下这么基本的错误吗。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1619
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_fc5fcd67:

    # "Damn.{p}How could we have made such a basic mistake?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3427,3428)
    "【柔一】\n「[西村]，[wdt]你先进去泡……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1620
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_49024c80:

    # ju "「[ln],{w=.2} you can go in first...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3428)
    ju "「[西村]，[wdt]你先进去泡……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1621
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_dae9ca59:

    # fn "「We made this together!\n It wouldn't be right if I get in first!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3433)
    fn "[漏れ]用坚定的语气打断了柔一说的话。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1622
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_54c1638c:

    # "I interrupt him with a strong tone."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3435,3436,3437)
    "【博行】\n「这个，[wdt]是[漏れ]和柔一一起做出来的！[l]\n只有[漏れ]先进去的话绝对不行！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1623
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_cf466977:

    # "Juuichi-san lets out a sigh.{p}He's like a father with his spoiled child.{p}...That might be true, in a sense."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3439,3440,3441)
    "柔一困扰地叹了口气。[l]\n简直就像是在耍赖的小孩面前的父亲似的。[l]\n……某种意味上可能真的是这样也不一定。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1624
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_c7469d1c:

    # ju "「Then what would you suggest?{p} Should I get in while holding you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3443,3444,3445)
    ju "【柔一】\n「……虽然这么说，[wdt]但是能怎么办呢？[l]\n难道要我抱着[西村]进去吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1625
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_9efa463f:

    # fn "「Sure, that sounds fine.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3447,3448)
    fn "【博行】\n「那就这么办吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1626
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_8055d932:

    # ju "「...You're right.{p} No matter what the circumstances...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3450,3451)
    ju "【柔一】\n「……对吧。[l]再怎么样也……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1627
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_06ba3a92:

    # "What I just said sinks in.{w=.2}\nJuuichi-san looks a little flustered."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3453,3454)
    "突然注意到[漏れ]说了什么，[wdt]\n柔一连忙往[漏れ]这里看了过来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1631
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_1941a44e:

    # ju "「...You're okay with that?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3458,3459)
    ju "【柔一】\n「……这样没关系吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1632
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b16bc932:

    # fn "「Of course.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3461,3462)
    fn "【博行】\n「当然。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1636
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_068947bf:

    # ju "「...I see.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3466,3467)
    ju "【柔一】\n「……是吗。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1637
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_190d3d38:

    # "Juuichi-san takes a deep breath.{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3469,3470)
    "呼。[wdt]柔一深深地叹了口气。[l][se 立ち上がる]\n不知是不是放弃争论了，柔一开始脱起了衣服。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1639
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_8f29f2d5:

    # extend "Did he make up his mind?\nHe's taking his clothes off."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3472,3473)
    extend "……毕竟是难得两人一起合力做的，[wdt]\n[漏れ]果然还是不希望只有自己一个人进去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1640
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_ae6ec2af:

    # "It seems my feelings got through to him.{w=.2}\n...Since both of us went through the trouble,\nI'd feel awkward being the only one getting in."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3475,3476)
    "想着想着很快地柔一就已经脱到全裸了。[l]\n[漏れ]也把剩下的内裤给脱了下来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1641
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_f4da8a7b:

    # "While I was thinking about this,\nJuuichi-san finishes getting undressed.{p}He's now completely nude."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3481,3482,3483)
    "虽然完全没有遮掩，但感觉却没有在海边那时觉得不好意思。[wdt]\n这是因为[漏れ]多少习惯了在别人面前裸露的关系吗。[l]\n……会习惯这种事情的人似乎有点糟糕就是了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1645
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_ade56c61:

    # "Though there's nothing concealing me,\nI'm not embarrassed."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3485,3486)
    "【博行】\n「柔一，[wdt]那[漏れ]们一起进去……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1646
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_477ef18c:

    # "Is it because of this liberating feeling\nI'm getting from being in nature?{p}...I wonder if I'm inclined towards exposure?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3493,3494,3495)
    "话讲到一半，突然间[漏れ]已经浮在空中了。[l]\n[漏れ]，[l]现在正被柔一，[l]那个，[l]该怎么说呢，[l]\n……这应该就是所谓的公主抱吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1647
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_a43280fb:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san, since the hot water-」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3497,3498)
    fn "【博行】\n「柔柔柔柔柔柔一！[wdt]　放[漏れ]下来啦！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1652
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_3823fa95:

    # "Suddenly, I find myself airborne,\nand my words get cut off."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3500,3501)
    "【柔一】\n「听不到。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1653
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_ea0b6ccd:

    # "I'm being carried in Juuichi-san's arms,\nlike a princess."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3503)
    "他咧开嘴角，[wdt]露出了牙齿。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1654
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_cfd7c895:

    # fn "「J-J-Juuichi-san!{w=.2} Please put me down!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3505-3506)
    fn "「不是说要一起进去吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1655
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b8190caf:

    # ju "「I can't hear you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3508,3509,3510)
    ju "被这么一说[漏れ]也没话可说了。[l]\n[漏れ]在柔一移动的时候，为了避免掉下来，[wdt]\n连忙紧紧抱住了他的脖子。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1656
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_50c5f601:

    # "The corner of his mouth curls up,{w=.2}\nshowing a fang."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3512,3513,3514)
    "柔一那有些汗湿的毛皮的触感，意外地感觉很舒服。[l]\n还想说会紧紧黏在[漏れ]的皮肤上的，[wdt]\n但结果碰到的感觉却很柔顺。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1657
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_bdf715fb:

    # ju "「Aren't we getting in together?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3518,3519,3520)
    ju "柔一走到手工露天温泉的中央坐了下来，[wdt]\n把[漏れ]的上半身转过去让[漏れ]坐到了他的两腿中间。[l]\n这个，[wdt]差不多就是让[漏れ]背靠在他的怀中给他抱着的姿势。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1658
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4952c43a:

    # "I'm at a loss for words.{p}...Even though I was the one who sowed these seeds,{w=.2}\nit feels like I've been outwitted by Juuichi-san."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3522)
    "下半身泡在热腾腾的温泉中的感觉既舒服又温暖。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1659
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_44e6df70:

    # "While thinking about that,{p}Juuichi-san walks towards our handmade bath.{w=.2}\nConfused, I cling to his neck."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3518-3520)
    "柔一走到手工露天温泉的中央坐了下来，[wdt]把[漏れ]的上半身转过去让[漏れ]坐到了他的两腿中间。[l]这个，[wdt]差不多就是让[漏れ]背靠在他的怀中给他抱着的姿势。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1663
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_26b93ea2:

    # "The feeling of fur damp with sweat is comfortable.\nI can also smell his sweat,\nbut it is by no means unpleasant."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3529,3530)
    "【柔一】\n「啊啊，[wdt]是啊……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1664
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_96d30ea7:

    # "Juuichi-san lowers himself into the bath,{w=.2}\ntwists the upper half of his body,\nand puts me between his legs."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3532)
    "就这样，[wdt][漏れ]们因为顾着享受温泉而沉默了下来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1665
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_667a03a5:

    # "He holds me as I sit with my hands around my knees."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3534,3535,3536)
    "一时间只听得到淙淙的溪水声和远方的蝉鸣。[l]\n以及眼前这既宽广又优美的自然风景。[l]\n一边泡着温泉一边欣赏着这些景致。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1666
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_f30e7eb6:

    # "I gradually feel the warmth of his lower body."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3538)
    "……总觉得，[漏れ][wdt]好像在做着某种非常奢侈的事的感觉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1670
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_c3dd10a5:

    # fn "「This feels really nice...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3540-3542)
    fn "「……[西村]。[l]这个姿势你不是另外还要出力吗，会不会累？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1671
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_2c73179a:

    # ju "「Yeah.{w=.2} it does...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3544,3545)
    ju "当[漏れ]正沉浸在眼前的风景中时，[wdt]\n柔一突然对[漏れ]说道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1672
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_2bd887a9:

    # "We appreciate the beautiful scenery\nbefore us for a while in silence."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3547,3548,3549)
    "为了不给柔一造成负担，[漏れ]尽可能把背挺直，\n让自己尽量不要靠在他身上，[l]\n不过看来完全被他看穿了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1673
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_e2220d0b:

    # "...It feels like I'm doing something luxurious."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3538)
    "……总觉得，[漏れ][wdt]好像在做着某种非常奢侈的事的感觉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1674
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_e00dbd4b:

    # ju "「...[ln].{w} Are you tired from all that\n unexpected hard work?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3554-3555)
    ju "「哇哇哇！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1675
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_546dbd40:

    # "While we're sitting and admiring the view,{w=.2}\nJuuichi-san asks me that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3559,3560,3561)
    "对这突然的动作[漏れ]完全无法反抗，[wdt]\n就这样往柔一身上倒了下去。[l]\n而柔一也温柔地抱住了[漏れ]。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1676
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4bd73e83:

    # "I straighten my back as much\nas I can so that I won't be a burden."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3563,3564)
    "【柔一】\n「不用顾虑那么多啦。[wdt]我和[西村]是朋友不是吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1677
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_652fd9a3:

    # "Even though I'm trying not to lean on him,\nit seems like he saw through me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3566,3567)
    "柔一在[漏れ]的耳边轻声说道。[l]\n……[漏れ]现在，[wdt]肯定是已经完全脸红了吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1678
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_d7f14872:

    # "Juuichi-san puts his hands on my shoulders,{p}and forces me to sit back down"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3569,3570)
    "【博行】\n「柔一……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1679
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_4b6799d8:

    # fn "「Waah!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3572,3573,3574)
    fn "虽然刚刚就已经觉得离得很近了，[wdt]\n但和现在的状况不能比。[l]零距离。[l]紧贴着。[l]\n整个背上，[wdt]都可以感受到和温泉不同的，柔一身上的温暖。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1683
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_7e60dc6e:

    # "Unable to resist his sudden action,{w=.2}\nI fall into him.{p}He gently embraces me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3576,3577)
    "【博行】\n「总觉得，[wdt]这样子的[漏れ]们好像爸爸跟小孩呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1684
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_8dda4425:

    # ju "「...{w=.2}Don't be so reserved.\n Don't we have a relationship?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3579)
    ju "为了隐藏害羞，[wdt][漏れ]便这么跟柔一说道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1685
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_c022fef4:

    # "He whispers into my ears.{p}....My face is definitely red now."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3581,3582)
    "【柔一】\n「……什么意思啊这个。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1686
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_998a3238:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3584,3585,3586)
    fn "【博行】\n「就字面上的意思啦。[l]柔一，[wdt]\n感觉好像是[漏れ]的爸爸似的呢……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1687
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_032f014c:

    # "I thought we were close earlier,{w=.2}\nbut now there's no distance between us.{p}Zero.{w} I'm stuck to him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3588,3589,3590)
    "[漏れ]转头一看，[wdt]差点吓了一跳。[l]\n柔一的脸，[wdt]\n比[漏れ]想象中还要靠得更近。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1688
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_3bf2d04a:

    # "On my back, I can feel his warmth.\nIt's different to the warmth of the hot spring."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3522)
    "下半身泡在热腾腾的温泉中的感觉既舒服又温暖。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1689
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_47d819e9:

    # fn "「We probably look like a\n parent and child doing this.」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3547)
    fn "为了不给柔一造成负担，[漏れ]尽可能把背挺直，[l]让自己尽量不要靠在他身上，[l]不过看来完全被他看穿了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1690
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_21b4a598:

    # "I talk to him in order to hide my embarrassment."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3600,3601)
    "【柔一】\n「……总觉得，[wdt]好像突然不好意思了起来。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1691
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_7263dd6e:

    # ju "「...What do you mean?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3603,3604)
    ju "柔一把身体稍微移远了一点。[l]\n这份关心让现在的[漏れ]更是觉得感激。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1692
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_7b198dc5:

    # fn "「It means just that.{w} Juuichi-san,{w=.2}\n you look like my father... Somehow.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3606,3607,3608)
    fn "【博行】\n「……抱歉。[l]\n总觉得总是在让柔一照顾呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1693
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_f8311e6f:

    # ju "「...Are you trying to say that I'm getting old?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3610,3611)
    ju "【柔一】\n「哎，[wdt]这就是我的责任啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1694
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_fd524db6:

    # fn "「Not at all.」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3608)
    fn "「……抱歉。[l]总觉得总是在让柔一照顾呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1695
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_1d0d35b7:

    # "I burst into laughter.\nJuuichi-san worries about something like that?\nThat's kind of cute."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3615,3616,3617)
    "啊啊，果然柔一的态度很像大人呢。[l]\n跟只会随着情绪做出反应的[漏れ]大不相同。[l]\n[漏れ]一边被摸着头，[wdt]一边这样想着。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1696
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b43d2661:

    # "When I turn my head to look over my shoulder,{w=.2}\nI'm startled at how close his face is."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3619,3620)
    "【柔一】\n「……责任，[wdt]吗。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1697
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_9cfa914a:

    # "If I just extend my body a little, we could kiss.\n...Wait, why am I thinking that?!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3622,3623)
    "柔一小声地喃喃念着的这句话，[wdt]\n一下子就融入溪水所发出的轻快溪流声而消散了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1698
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_ff62d27b:

    # "Embarrassed, I quickly look away.{p}My neck cracks,{w=.2}\nbut I'm too worried about other things."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3596-3598)
    "因为不好意思的关系，[漏れ]连忙将头转了开来。[l]虽然听到脖子发出喀的声音，[wdt]不过现在不是在意那种事的时候了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1699
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_cb7d578b:

    # ju "「...What are you being so shy about now?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3628,3629,3630)
    ju "【柔一】\n「啊，没事。[l]\n不必在意。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1700
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_ea3c9d05:

    # "I feel him let go of me a little.{p}I'm thankful for his consideration."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3604)
    "柔一把身体稍微移远了一点。[l]这份关心让现在的[漏れ]更是觉得感激。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1701
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b9cc2d9a:

    # fn "「...Sorry.{p} I didn't mean to make you worry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3636,3637)
    fn "【博行】\n「哎呀，[wdt]已经这个时候了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1702
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_08588aa1:

    # ju "「I don't mind.{w=.2} That's my role as a senior.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3639,3640,3641)
    ju "花在挖温泉上的时候比想象来得多，[wdt]\n结果能泡温泉的时间反而变少了吗。[l]\n有点可惜呢。[l]如果能早点把温泉挖出来就好了呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1703
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_e54558a5:

    # "He pats me on the head as he says that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3613)
    "柔一用力地揉了揉[漏れ]的头。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1704
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_f94d33fb:

    # "Aah, he is an adult after all.{p}I think about this as he pats my head."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3646,3647)
    "【博行】\n「柔一，[wdt]疲劳有消除了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1705
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_e6ed7118:

    # ju "「...It's my duty.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3619,3620)
    ju "【柔一】\n「……责任，[wdt]吗。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1706
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_38458475:

    # "He mutters something,{w=.2}\nbut most of it is lost to the sound of the stream."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3622,3623)
    "柔一小声地喃喃念着的这句话，[wdt]\n一下子就融入溪水所发出的轻快溪流声而消散了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1707
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_5538a264:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3625,3626)
    fn "【博行】\n「柔一？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1708
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_025e7188:

    # ju "「Oh, it's nothing.\n Never mind.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3628,3629,3630)
    ju "【柔一】\n「啊，没事。[l]\n不必在意。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1709
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_9d615cb6:

    # ju "「Well,we should be getting up soon.\n Everyone will worry about us if we're late.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3632,3633,3634)
    ju "【柔一】\n「那么，[wdt]差不多也该起来了。[l]\n要是太晚回去的话大家会担心的。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1710
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_b21ad983:

    # fn "「You're right, let's get up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3636,3637)
    fn "【博行】\n「哎呀，[wdt]已经这个时候了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1711
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_2e5eb5c8:

    # "I'd completely lost track of time.{w=.2}\nI wish we could have spent longer here,\nbut Juuichi-san is right."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3639,3640,3641)
    "花在挖温泉上的时候比想象来得多，[wdt]\n结果能泡温泉的时间反而变少了吗。[l]\n有点可惜呢。[l]如果能早点把温泉挖出来就好了呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1712
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_eeb02e49:

    # "We get out of the bath,{w=.2}\n{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3643,3644)
    "[漏れ]们从露天温泉中出来，[wdt][se 立ち上がる]\n用毛巾擦干身体，开始穿起衣服。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1714
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_0d90fa06:

    # extend "and I start to dry myself off with my towel."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3643,3644)
    extend "[漏れ]们从露天温泉中出来，[wdt][se 立ち上がる]\n用毛巾擦干身体，开始穿起衣服。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1715
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_d7116955:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san,{w=.2} did that help your fatigue?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3646,3647)
    fn "【博行】\n「柔一，[wdt]疲劳有消除了吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1716
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_f8581d2d:

    # "While pulling my shirt on,{w=.2}\nI ask him that, pretending it was nothing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3649,3650)
    "[漏れ]一边套着上衣，[wdt]\n一边假装没事地问道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1717
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_da126a8d:

    # "I mean, I did come here with that goal in mind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3652,3653)
    "因为最后发生的事情而差点忘记了，[wdt]\n但一开始是为了能想柔一消除疲劳才跟过来的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1718
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_778ce8ce:

    # "If I just made him even more tired...{p}That would suck."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3655,3656)
    "要是反而让他的疲劳不减反增的话……[l]\n那可实在是太对不起他了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1722
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_42fff913:

    # ju "「...Yeah,{w=.2} it did.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3661,3662)
    ju "【柔一】\n「……啊啊，[wdt]也是呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1723
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_a07f158b:

    # fn "「Then, I wasn't a bother to you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3664,3665)
    fn "【博行】\n「[漏れ]，[wdt]应该没有造成麻烦吧？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1727
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_5de28dbc:

    # ju "「...Are you thinking about before?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3669,3670)
    ju "【柔一】\n「……你觉得就算有我会在本人面前说吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1728
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_a81afae7:

    # "Juuichi-san smiles wryly.{p}Ooh, that was definitely it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3672,3673)
    "柔一苦笑了起来。[l]\n呜，[wdt]这么说确实是没错啦……"

# game/day 15.rpy:1732
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_9b97e425:

    # ju "「Every once in a while,{w=.2}\n it's all right to let one's\n hair down with someone else.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3678,3679,3680)
    ju "【柔一】\n「……像这样，[wdt]偶尔和谁一起出来\n轻松地游玩似乎也挺不错的。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1736
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_cc8c6a94:

    # "Saying no more than that, he quickly looks away.\nThank you, Juuichi-san..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3684)
    "柔一说着把脸转了过去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:1737
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_94a1c0ac:

    # ju "「Let's go,{w=.2} [ln].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3686,3687)
    ju "【柔一】\n「好了，[wdt]赶快穿好衣服回去吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1738
translate chinese_simplified camp15_juuichi_d2894ecc:

    # fn "「W-{w=.2}wait a minute, Juuichi-san!\n You still haven't put your shirt on!」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3690)
    fn "「啊，[wdt]等[漏れ]一下啦，柔一！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1751
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_55fd8fbd:

    # "I wonder what Shin-kun is going to do?{p}Somehow, I can't see him saying 'exploring'."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3705,3706,3707)
    "深君打算做什么呢。[l]\n他可不是会喊出「探险！」的类型，\n应该是像平常一样看书等等，[wdt]这一类的吧？"

# game/day 15.rpy:1752
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_006b7b8c:

    # "Isn't he usually doing something like reading?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3713,3714)
    "【博行】\n「深君要做什么呢？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1758
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_b58ace86:

    # fn "「Shin-kun, what are you doing?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3714)
    fn "「深君要做什么呢？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1759
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_e7b2e189:

    # si "「Me?{p} I haven't decided on anything in particular.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3717)
    si "「我？[l]还没决定耶。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1764
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_32346b10:

    # ko "「Oh,{w=.2} if that's the case-」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3724)
    ko "「啊，[wdt]这样的话――」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1768
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_5c5a84ba:

    # si "「No thank you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3730)
    si "「不要。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1772
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_003f2c3b:

    # ko "「Hey!{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3736)
    ko "「太快了吧！[l][孝之助 困惑 normal][wt]我还什么都没说呢。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1774
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_c1a9062d:

    # extend "I haven't even said anything yet...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3746,3747)
    extend "【博行】\n「确实……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1779
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_43b57dc6:

    # si "「None of your suggestions has ever\n led to a pleasant experience.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3743)
    si "「既然是孝之助的提案，[l]那肯定有什么不良企图。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1780
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_b8acbdc8:

    # fn "「That's true...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3786)
    fn "「是啊。[wdt]那时候还跟他说只是要苹果的话就给你算了的。[l]不过犯人似乎因为体重相当重的关系，[wdt]后来压断苹果树枝之后逃走了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1781
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_69058d77:

    # ko "「What's with you two today?{w=.2}\n It's like I'm some sort of troublemaker.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3762,3763)
    ko "【孝之助】\n「才没有那种事呢！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:1787
translate chinese_simplified camp15_shin_b050fba6:

    # to "「Well, it's true, isn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 3750)
