# game/day 15.rpy:2937
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_99f93009:

    # to "「Oh, isn't it a shame to hide?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 682)
    to "「啊，[l]遮住也太狡猾了！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2938
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_582ed7a2:

    # fn "「I wonder who caused all of this!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 685)
    fn "「因为谁知道会发生这种事啊！！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2944
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_f3819459:

    # to "「Oh, that's right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 693)
    to "「啊，也是哦」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2945
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_ecefe952:

    # "Torahiko seems to remember something, then he takes out a folding knife for camping from his dry pants pocket."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 695)
    "虎彦好像想到了什么，从干着的裤子口袋里拿出一把露营用的折叠刀。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2949
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_3e9d7144:

    # to "「Let's prepare the fish we just caught and bake it on\n the bonfire.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 701)
    to "「把刚才钓到的鱼，放在篝火上烤吧」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2950
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_69edbbd1:

    # "Then, he takes out the fish from the cage and begins to cut it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 703)
    "这么说着，虎彦从小池塘里抓起一只鱼开始处理。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2951
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_307758df:

    # "As expected, Torahiko's really good at cooking, so he takes out the internal organs of the fish without any difficulty."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 705)
    "像平常一样地开始料理，利落地取出鱼的内脏。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2952
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_91621453:

    # "Then, the fish were skewered with some shaved tree branches."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 708)
    "然后用削过皮的树枝把鱼串起来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2956
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_ba8a19c1:

    # to "「Well, I'm glad that I happened to have salt in my\n bag.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 712)
    to "「还记得把盐放进背包里，真是太好了」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2957
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_53ebb3bc:

    # "Said Torahiko, who took out the bottle of salt that was used in yesterday's cooking from his bag, sprinkled it evenly, and sets it on the bonfire."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 714)
    "这么说来，虎彦昨天用的料理材料是从自己的背包里面拿出来的。取出精盐瓶，均匀地把盐撒上去，然后立在篝火旁。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2962
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_7de8afa3:

    # "..... About 20 minutes later."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 722)
    "……20分钟后。[l]离火稍微远点的烤鱼滴下了油脂，吱吱作响地发出美味的声音。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2963
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_feb96d81:

    # "The fish, which has been slowly roasted over a long fire, is dripping and making a delicious noise."
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 722)
    "……20分钟后。[l]离火稍微远点的烤鱼滴下了油脂，吱吱作响地发出美味的声音。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2967
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_bd2c5e1b:

    # to "「It looks good.{w} Let's eat!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 728)
    to "「好，已经好了。[l][博行]，来吃吧」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2968
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_fb273f47:

    # fn "「Yeah, let's eat!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 731)
    fn "「嗯，[漏れ]要开动了」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2969
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_7cf3f15c:

    # "I take a bite ..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 733)
    "内脏被完全取出，只剩下鱼肚的部分。啊嗯……"

# game/day 15.rpy:2970
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_7eed507d:

    # fn "「.....{w} It's so delicious!!{w} It really is!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 738)
    fn "「……好吃！！[l]原来香鱼这么好吃的吗……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2971
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_481deb19:

    # "Right the moment of biting, I feel the crispy texture of the outer skin, while the meat is very soft and fluffy, which melts in my mouth immediately."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 741)
    "咬下去的那一瞬间，外皮的部分如此酥脆。这是什么样的口感，身体的部分很饱满、很蓬松地在口中化开。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2972
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_22a4be90:

    # "The juiciness of the fish itself stands out while the mellow taste rushes into my mouth."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 745)
    "鱼本身的多汁凸显了这美味，然后温和的鲜味进入口中。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2973
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_60f1e9d4:

    # to "「Really?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 749)
    to "「是嘛，是嘛」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2974
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_51d38ac3:

    # "Torahiko bites the fish that he's holding on the skewer from the side."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 751)
    "[漏れ]拿着的这一串，虎彦从另一边咬一口。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2978
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_4f861f97:

    # to "「Yeah, it tastes really good!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 755)
    to "「嗯，感觉不错」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2979
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_7d4e1513:

    # fn "「You are really a chef, aren't you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 758)
    fn "「意料之中呢，虎彦大厨」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2983
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_c874ee40:

    # to "「Nah, it's just like an instant dish to me.{w} I\n literally just took out the internal organs and\n sprinkled it with salt.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 762)
    to "「因为没做好充分准备，所以算不上是料理。[l]只不过是把内脏拿掉，洒了点盐罢了」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2984
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_74ebc66b:

    # fn "「Yeah, but it's really delicious.{w} Therefore, I\n decide to forgive you for having dragged me into the\n water earlier.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 766)
    fn "「是吗？[l]不过真的很好吃喔。[l][漏れ]原谅被你拉入水中的事」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2988
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_eca046d2:

    # to "「Heheh, that's clearly what I'm trying to do here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 770)
    to "「嘿～嘿～就是这样啦」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2989
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_6ebe73b7:

    # "The two of us just laugh at each other.{w} It's so much fun to be self-sufficient in the wilderness."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 773)
    "两人相视而笑。在自然界自给自足还真是好玩。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2990
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_44cba9bb:

    # "Although it's fun to spend time together at the campsite,{w} it feels like survival here and it's a different kind of fun to be honest."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 777)
    "虽然在露营场跟大家一起玩也很有趣，但这里有种野外生存的感觉，有种不一样的快乐。"

# game/day 15.rpy:2996
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_3ee49bf2:

    # to "「Well...{w} Our clothes are dry, we should put out the\n fire and head back.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 787)
    to "「好了……[l]衣服也干了，把火灭了就离开吧」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2997
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_618bce59:

    # fn "「That's right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 790)
    fn "「说的也是」"

# game/day 15.rpy:2998
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_0f4eb24e:

    # "We put our clothes, which smell like a mini bonfire, back on and return to the original path."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 792)
    "[漏れ]穿回身上沾了点篝火味的衣服，沿原路返回。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3004
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_e63e7146:

    # to "「Ugh, are we going through this cave again...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 801)
    to "「唔啊，还要通过这个洞窟啊……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3005
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_9847d5ec:

    # fn "「It isn't scary, is it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 804)
    fn "「……果然虎彦，在害怕吧？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3006
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_1f21181a:

    # to "「Tch, but...{w} It's dangerous because it's really\n dark.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 807)
    to "「才，[l]才——不是！[l]只是，[l]那个……[l]因为很暗所以很危险…」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3007
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_278e041d:

    # fn "「Yeah, yeah.{w} See you then.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 811)
    fn "「啊～是是。[l]好吧，[l]那来吧」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3008
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_631147e7:

    # "Torahiko immediately wraps his arm around my waist and holds my hand."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 813)
    "跟虎彦并行，[漏れ]伸出了手臂，握住了虎彦的手。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3009
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_522315fa:

    # fn "「Will doing that reduce the risk by any chance?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 817)
    fn "「这样危险度就稍微降低了吧？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3010
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_d2f149b4:

    # to "「Gulp...{w} That's right.{w} A bit safer.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 820)
    to "「唔……[l]是，[l]是啊。[l]感觉安全一点了」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3011
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_61e92d40:

    # "After saying, he holds my body even tighter with his hands."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 822)
    "虎彦紧握着[漏れ]的手，身体向[漏れ]的方向靠过来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3012
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_91d5f759:

    # "We move forward.{w} From the touching point, I can feel Torahiko's body trembling.{w} Wow, he's cute already."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 825)
    "从接触的地方，可以感受到虎彦的身体在颤抖。[l]真是，可爱啊。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3013
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_701e8962:

    # fn "「Alright, let's go.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 830)
    fn "「好的，那出发咯」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3014
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_517d4eb0:

    # to "「O-Okay...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 833)
    to "「哦，喔……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3015
translate chinese_simplified camp15_torahiko_28c4ed6e:

    # "Of course, after that, we were able to return to the campsite without any dangerous happenings."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 835)
    "当然之后没发生危险的事，顺利地回到了营地。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3034
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_5bf684f5:

    # to "「Let's start cleaning up...!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    to "开始收拾吧！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3038
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_5a61fca5:

    # ky "「We won't be finished before the day is over,\n so we'll be going home in the middle of the night.{p} Stay alert.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ky "直到今天结束，我们的旅程才算画上句号，所以大概会在半夜时往回返。请格外注意。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3042
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_f69e5f92:

    # so "「All right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    so "好！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3047
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_3cb35517:

    # ta "「The baggage is the same as when we got here,\n so we'll be able to get it on the truck easily.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "行李还是来的时候的那些东西，所以只要搬回卡车上就OK了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3051
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_3181cf83:

    # ju "「I can carry the heavy things...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ju "我可以拿沉的东西……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3055
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_85104af8:

    # su "「I can help too!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "我也来帮忙！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3056
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_7642571b:

    # ju "「Kodori... go ask over there.{p} It looks like they don't have enough help.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ju "古酉……你还是去那边帮忙吧。似乎那边更需要你的帮助。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3060
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_6135a876:

    # su "「Am I not good enough?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "我不能帮你搬东西吗？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3061
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_497e4780:

    # "The luggage is too much for Shun-kun.{p}On the other hand, he might be able to carry it on\nthe way back."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "峻君帮忙搬行李什么的就太超越想象了，那东西对他来说，真是太巨大了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3062
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_9201ecd4:

    # fn "「Physical labor is impossible for me too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "[咱]也不擅长体力劳动呐~"

# game/day 15.rpy:3067
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_1c4ff3d1:

    # si "「Is it impossible, or do you just not want to do it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    si "是不擅长，还是懒得做呢？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3068
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_e120432b:

    # fn "「Th-{w=.2}that's not it, you're the one who doesn't\n want to do it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "才、才不是那样呐，深君你才是根本不想做吧？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3069
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_ec40078a:

    # si "「That may be, but there is a thing called\n 'the right person in the right place'.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    si "或许如此，但是有句话是说“人尽其材，物尽其用”。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3070
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_9f98c789:

    # si "「Would you really say that physical\n labor is suitable for me?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    si "你觉得我适合体力劳动吗？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3071
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_4ef7bf34:

    # fn "「That's not it...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "不适合。。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3075
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_53777672:

    # si "「Fine then...{p} If I get another asthma attack,\n are you going to take responsibility?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    si "而且……要是我因此而哮喘发作，你能负得起这个责任吗？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3076
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_15f01aa7:

    # fn "「W-{w=.2}wait, Shin-kun.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "等、等一下，深君"

# game/day 15.rpy:3083
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_a6d5aa57:

    # ta "「Shin, you look like you're in a good mood.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "深，你看起来心情不错嘛。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3084
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_def9dd63:

    # ka "「Is it because he's come out to play?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ka "大概是一起出去玩得很开心吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3090
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_366b2a74:

    # "When the air is nice, the sky looks beautiful.{p}Everything has been put away,\nand there's nothing left to do."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "空气沁人心脾，放眼长空如洗。似乎无论何事，都可顷刻间释然，只需仰望，无需再做其他的事。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3091
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "……。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3092
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_92a819b8:

    # "In just a short time we'll be done with camping..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "然后，短暂的露营，就这样结束了……。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3096
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_d039669c:

    # "Today is the 15th, so I'm\nnow in the second half of my\nstay at Minasato..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "今天是15号，[漏れ]在水乡村的时间只剩下后半月了……。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3097
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_abf9e464:

    # "That was fast."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "时间过得真快。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3098
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_abad5222:

    # "Because there's only half left,\nI wish I could stay in the village longer."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "只剩下半个月啦，真希望能再多待一段时间。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3099
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_2beef6dc:

    # "Well, we're returning..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "我们回去了……。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3100
translate chinese_simplified camp15_packup_4cbe89e4:

    # "Huh?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "哦呀？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3117
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_8721e6d1:

    # ta "「What are you doing here?{p} Let's get back to the village.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "你们在这儿做啥呢？我们快回村子里吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3118
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_966f18ca:

    # fn "「Tatsu-nii...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "辰兄……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3122
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_0d2eb345:

    # ta "「What is it? Is something wrong?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "怎么了？发生什么事了吗？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3123
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_3fe88462:

    # fn "「Well.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "那个……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3124
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_0f867a4b:

    # fn "「I was thinking about the second half of my vacation\n in Minasato and got kind of lonely.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "我只是在想，不知不觉我的水乡村假期已经过半，莫名地觉得寂寞忧伤。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3128
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_29cb32ad:

    # ta "「Idiot. You're only halfway, right?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "什么啊笨蛋。明明还有一半的时间不是吗！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3129
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_83aff416:

    # fn "「But the first half went by so quickly.{p} It would be bad if I didn't notice that until the\n day I go home.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "但是前半月真是过得太快了。如果直到回家的那天我才意识到的话，岂不是太槽糕了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3133
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_a6aecce7:

    # ta "「What are you standing there feeling all alone for.{p} Try to remember that half that went by so fast.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "为什么要一个人在那儿想什么寂寞之类的事情呀。这半个月不会只记得匆匆过这种事情了吧！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3134
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_d4be5178:

    # ta "「There was your welcoming party, our trip to the beach,\n and we camped today.{p} Haven't you also been playing and working at my house?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "欢迎会啊，海边旅行，还有这次的露营。还有，你不也在我家玩和工作过吗？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3135
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_ea4d65d0:

    # fn "「And we're putting together an airplane.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "还有一起做飞机。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3139
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_196b4cdc:

    # ta "「That's right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "对嘛！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3140
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_1c7a8154:

    # ta "「And with all that, there's also the second half.{p} Think of all the fun things ahead. Gahaha!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "这样的生活还有一半没过哪。优先考虑开心的事情才对嘛。嘎哈哈——"

# game/day 15.rpy:3141
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_e32d16c1:

    # fn "「But it's going to be hard to go back home.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "这样一想的话，完全不想回家了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3145
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_02750d6f:

    # ta "「Then come back in Winter.{p} And if that's not enough, come back in Spring too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "那就冬天再来玩嘛。如果还玩不够，春天再来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3149
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_64e4b348:

    # ta "「If you say you can't come,\n then I'll come running, any time.{w} It's\n likely I'll get my dad's fist afterwards, though.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "如果你说你不能来的话，我就追你到天涯海角……就算之后会挨我爹的一顿老拳。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3150
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_8a46c352:

    # fn "「Wow, that's reliable.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "哇哦，那倒是很可能会……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3154
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_3a79fa60:

    # ta "「So don't worry about what's ahead.{p} Just enjoy Minasato as much as you can now.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "别担心那些有的没的了。只需要享受现在的水乡村生活就足够了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3155
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_a2d35197:

    # ta "「If you don't, even the things you like become dull.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "不然的话，现在做的事情也会变味的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3156
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_7b78ab74:

    # fn "「Thanks, Tatsu-nii. I'm feeling better.{p} You're right, thinking about that would be a loss.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "谢谢你，辰兄。现在我打起精神来了。你说得对，想太多反而不好。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3160
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_d603bb57:

    # ta "「It would.{p} Besides, I might eventually go to the city too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "是啊。而且啊，我倒是真的有可能也会追去都市呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3161
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_e2cf3886:

    # fn "「What, you're also leaving Minasato?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "诶诶，辰兄打算离开水乡村？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3165
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_15f05760:

    # ta "「Yeah, I'll probably have to leave sooner or later to\n continue my training. But I've still got plenty of my\n apprenticeship left, so that's a few years away yet.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "是啊，我早晚都有可能会外出继续我的修行深造。但是我离完成学徒的修行还差很多，还有挺长的路要走。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3166
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_17c0f677:

    # fn "「Then you might be closer to me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "也就是说，以后辰兄可能会在离[漏れ]很近的地方。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3170
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_2f18d89a:

    # ta "「Well, you never know what lies ahead.{p} To become a man, it would be bad to not leave home once.{p} But I will come back to carry on the family business.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "未来倒是未知的。不过不管怎么说，作为男人，总呆在家中也不像个样。但是我最终还是会回来接手家里的工作就是了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3174
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_f1ade401:

    # ta "「[fn], what about you?{p} What are you going to do in the future?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "[博行]，你呢？你以后想做什么呢？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3175
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_1819a4e7:

    # fn "「Hmmm... I'm not sure.{p} First of all, I'll go to college.{w} Of course what you're\n doing is what you always talked about in the past.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "诶，那个……我也不知道。总之先会去上大学吧。但是辰兄倒是仍然追逐着曾经多次提及的那个未来呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3179
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_4a54e6a1:

    # ta "「Yes, to become the best craftsman in Japan.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "当然了，一定要成为日本第一职人。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3180
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_f3f7044b:

    # fn "「It's nice that you have a goal.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "有一个目标，真好。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3184
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_26dfd888:

    # ta "「I get lucky with these kind of things,\n so I ended up figuring it out faster than the others.{p} I think you'll find something if you look carefully.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "我只是碰巧和梦想离得比较近罢了，所以比别人先考虑到这些。我觉得你也可以找到你想要的，只要你留些心。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3185
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_c93b5f23:

    # fn "「Yeah. I wonder what I should do.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "这样啊。[漏れ]在想，[咱]的目标又是什么呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3189
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_22e96abb:

    # ta "「If you have nowhere to go, come to my house,\n and you'll be accepted immediately.{w} If I have to,\n I'll even use my authority as the next boss.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "如果你无处可去的话，不如就来我家吧。保证直接录用。就算让我用上少主的职权，也没有问题。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3190
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_d9447710:

    # fn "「Hahaha, I'll think about it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "哈哈，那我考虑考虑。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3194
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_ef48f976:

    # ta "「You'll get the job whether or not the\n business side decides it.{w} That's because\n they don't have the right to put you on hold.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "如果去别处找工作的话，能不能被录用都是未知数吧。难得的好机会喔。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3195
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_f8005260:

    # fn "「First of all, I'd have to choose where to interview.{p} I wonder if I'd be profitible for the Midoriya Group...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "我想，首先得决定好去怎样的地方面试才行吧。我不太确定留在翠屋组是否有前途……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3199
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_3138acdc:

    # ta "「Don't say that. What we're talking about, I'll make\n sure dad definitely hears all about it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "说什么呢。这种话，我要说给我老爸听一次看看啊……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3200
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_9479978d:

    # fn "「Th-{w=.2}that's okay. You don't need to go that far...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "抱、抱歉。还是别让他听到比较好……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3204
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_aace837f:

    # ta "「Heh, I understand, I understand.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "好啦好啦，不会让他知道的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3208
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_06a55ffb:

    # ta "「Well, I won't ask for your help at my house tomorrow.{p} Same goes for the airplane, though it was pretty\n tiring to work on by myself.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "好啦，明天开始，家里的工作还请多多关照。飞机的事情，也期待你多来帮忙，自己一个人修挺无聊的……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3209
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_cdd8728d:

    # fn "「I'll leave it to you then, it's gotten to\n the point where you're doing a good job on it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "放心吧，我现在已经很能干了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3213
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_2008e35e:

    # ta "「That's nice of you to say,\n even though it's not ready to fly yet.{p} It really is a pain.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "说得真好听，明明连工房都还没来过呢。真是受不了你啊。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3214
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_a74955a4:

    # fn "「Eheheh.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "诶嘿嘿。。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3218
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_a3c95893:

    # ta "「Well then, we should get back.{p} If we keep talking here,\n everybody's going to worry about us.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "好了，是时候回去啦。再这样待下去，其他人会担心的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3222
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_45ac1af5:

    # "Tatsu-nii says that, then turns around to\nwalk back towards everyone.{p}I follow behind him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "辰兄说完，转过脸朝大家所在的方向走去。[漏れ]也不想回得太晚，于是紧跟了上去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3223
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_8074338a:

    # fn "「Yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "哇。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3224
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_40f59153:

    # "Let's go back to Minasato."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "一起回到水乡村。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3225
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_eef7290f:

    # "The Amaryllis buds have begun to swell, showing that\nthe peak of Summer is declining."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "彼岸花开始绽放，提醒人们夏日已经降临。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3226
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_71e97537:

    # "My summer vacation has reached that point too,\nbut I shouldn't think about that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "[漏れ]的暑假已经过半，但是我不会再去想它了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3227
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_4a1427de:

    # "I don't know what's going to happen,\nso I'll make sure to enjoy this year's summer,\nsince it only happens once."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "不知道未来会发生什么，所以只需要享受此夏便好，因为它仅此一次。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3231
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_6b90f356:

    # ta "「[fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "[博行]"

# game/day 15.rpy:3232
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_b5fb207e:

    # fn "「What?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "怎么了？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3236
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_878fa674:

    # ta "「When the airplane is completed,\n we're going to fly together.{p} Don't forget.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "飞机完成之后，一起飞上天哦。别忘记这个约定。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3237
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_898a6913:

    # fn "「Yeah, let's try our best.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "嗯，加油啊！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3238
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_46270019:

    # "The second half..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "这后半个月……。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3239
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_fae381eb:

    # "I'll enjoy it as much as I can."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "我要珍惜并享受每一天。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3243
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_a51111f6:

    # ta "「All right then.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "没错。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3244
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_40aef6a0:

    # fn "「Ah, that's dangerous Tatsu-nii.\n There's a cliff over there!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "啊，那里危险，辰兄。会掉下去！！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3248
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_22147849:

    # ta "「What!? Ah... WAAAAAAAAAAH!! [fn]!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    ta "诶！？啊……哇噢噢噢噢噢噢噢，[博行]ー！！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3253
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_tatsuki_3e87746a:

    # fn "「Tatsu-nii!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "辰兄————！！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3266
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_786d39ce:

    # su "「[fn]-san.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "[博行]桑。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3267
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_5104d70b:

    # fn "「Shun-kun?{w=.2} What's wrong?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "峻君？怎么了？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3271
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_12095ffe:

    # su "「It's already time to go back, isn't it...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "已经要回去了呢……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3272
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_c8e69220:

    # "His shoulders drop.{p}I see, since he got to play with everybody for two full days,\nhe's reluctant to go back."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "峻的肩膀垂了下来。这样啊，是对在这里住的两天还有跟大家一起玩的那些事情，觉得很意犹未尽啊。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3273
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_85bc3d9f:

    # fn "「That's right, we have to.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "就是啊，不想回去啊。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3274
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_c54f850d:

    # "He has sad eyes and a dropping tail.{p}Shun-kun smiles at my words but also hangs his head down."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "寂寞的眼神。下垂的尾巴。[漏れ]笑着低下头来对着峻君说。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3275
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_d8fa5837:

    # fn "「Still, you're coming with everybody, right?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "还想跟着大家再来这吗？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3276
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_c4fced84:

    # "I pet his head.{p}Usually, he would reply with an energetic response.{p}His brown coat is stained red with the setting sun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "[漏れ]拍了拍峻君的头。本该是相当有精神地回答着「我们回去吧」此时却不是如此。茶色的毛皮被夕阳给染成了红色。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3277
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_aa447ced:

    # fn "「Are you sad?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "会寂寞吗？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3278
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_1bb4b62a:

    # su "「Yes...{w=.2}but I did get to take a bath with everybody,\n and I got to sleep and wake up early\n with you, Tatsuki-san, and Ko-ya-san.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "是的……因为，在盥洗后，睡觉然后早上起来的时候有[博行]桑、辰樹桑、还有洸哉桑在，"

# game/day 15.rpy:3279
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_7fe3d57a:

    # su "「But everything will go back to the way it was tomorrow.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "不过明天就都回归原来的生活了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3280
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_3bafa0ee:

    # fn "「I'm sad too.{p} But I'll still get to have fun with everybody, right?{p} There's going to be the festival at Minasato's shrine.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "[漏れ]也觉得很寂寞啊。不过还是能够跟大家一起玩的吧？对了，水乡神社还会举办一场祭典的对吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3281
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_ab89c007:

    # su "「Y-yeah...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "是、是的……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3282
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_2e392636:

    # fn "「So don't look like that.{p} Did you have fun camping?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "别摆出那种表情。来露营，是很快乐的吧？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3286
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_cc34fb99:

    # su "「Yes! {w=.2}I got to play a lot!{p} I also got to hear a lot of stories,\n but there's still something I don't understand...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "是！玩得相当的尽兴！也听到了很多事，虽然还是有听不懂的事情……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3287
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_4d20f0c7:

    # "I-is he talking about that obscene thing from yesterday?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    "是、是昨天那段儿童不宜的事情吧？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3288
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_eb7a5bd6:

    # fn "「If you really didn't understand, I'll tell you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "不懂的事情之后我再教你好了，好吗？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3289
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_e0dc7172:

    # su "「Thank you very much!{w=.2}{nw} "
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "谢谢！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3291
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_f7bd2e24:

    # extend "{w=.2}Woof!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    extend "哇呼！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3292
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_72c0fb5c:

    # fn "「Still, I have half of my summer vacation left?{p} I haven't talked or played enough with you.{p} There's still plenty of time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "暑假可是还剩下一半喔？不管是还没有聊到的事情，还是还没有玩到的东西。可是还有一大堆呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3293
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_e4d6cc45:

    # fn "「So tomorrow will just be getting back to my vacation.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "明天啊只是回归到「原本的」暑假而已啊。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3297
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_aa3050be:

    # su "「...{w=.2} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3299
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_08b317cd:

    # extend "Yeah!{w=.2} Okay!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    extend "是的！我知道了！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3300
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_99cec631:

    # fn "「Are you feeling better now?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    fn "不会觉得寂寞了吧？"

# game/day 15.rpy:3301
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_460c8ed0:

    # su "「Yes! {w=.2}I still get to do\n plenty of fun things with you!{p} And everybody else!{w} So I'm already not sad!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "是的！因为还有更多好玩的事情，跟[博行]一起玩更多的东西！跟大家一起玩更多的东西！所以，已经不觉得寂寞了！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3305
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shun_e5645a92:

    # su "「[fn]-san, I like you so much-♪」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks
    su "我最喜欢[博行]桑了！"

# game/day 15.rpy:3316
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_8e0f55ef:

    # "Somebody approaches me from behind.{p}The Sun behind me makes a glare,\nso I'm not sure who it is."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5584-5585)
    "对面有谁在接近。\n他背后的太阳太过眩目，看不清楚是谁。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3317
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_dde83c31:

    # "That's..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5587)
    "那个是……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3321
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_7c659639:

    # fn "「Kouya...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5592-5593)
    fn "「洸哉……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3322
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_b6f1c49b:

    # "My eyes gradually adjust\nand I can see who it is."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5595)
    "在眼睛慢慢习惯后就明白了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3323
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_fc6b66d7:

    # "He walks up straight up to me and\nasks me a question."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5597-5598)
    "洸哉就那样直接走到了[漏れ]的面前。\n然后问道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3324
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_559294ce:

    # ka "「What are you doing in a place like this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5600-5601)
    ka "「你在这种地方做什么呢？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3325
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_f8f783ab:

    # fn "「Mm... {w=.2}I was feeling a little sentimental.{p} My summer vacation is already halfway over.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5603-5605)
    fn "「啊……稍微有点沉浸在感伤里。\n夏天不是已经过了一半了么。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3326
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_fdd87fcb:

    # fn "「It feels like it's going faster than usual.{p} Time really has passed in the blink of an eye.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5607-5609)
    fn "「总觉得比平常过得更快啊。\n真的是一眨眼就过去了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3327
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_ae43d6ee:

    # "When half of it was over,{w=.2}\n'There's still another half. I've got time,'\nis what I imagined I would be thinking."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5611-5612)
    "到现在为止的暑假过完一半的时候，都会有\n「还剩下一半啊，真闲呐」这样的想法。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3328
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_9019a0ae:

    # "Since it's hot, I didn't bother going outside much.{p}I just sat around in the house all day."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5614-5615)
    "因为太热了，不是很愿意到外面去。\n一整天都会在家里面滚来滚去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3329
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_9ea3f506:

    # "However, time keeps flowing,\nand my vaction keeps moving on."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5616)
    "只有时间流逝，除此之外什么都没有的暑假。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3330
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_d6b1d6e9:

    # "But there is no room for\nthose feelings in this summer."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5618)
    "但是只有这个暑假，完全没有那样的心情。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3331
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_519500ac:

    # "I also can't be wasting time.{p}There are so many things I want to-{w=.2}\nNo, have to do."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5619-5620)
    "没有时间浪费。\n有很多想要做的――不、要做的事情。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3332
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_62fa9201:

    # "So I become filled with even more deep emotion."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5622)
    "所以感慨变得更深了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3333
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_2a5507eb:

    # ka "「You're right...{p} I also think this year's\n summer has gone by quickly.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5625-5626)
    ka "「说的也是……\n今年夏天，我也觉得过得很快。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3334
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_32102c10:

    # fn "「You too?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5629)
    fn "「洸哉也？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3335
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_a97a0e2a:

    # ka "「Yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5632)
    ka "「啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3339
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_87aab42f:

    # "With just that short response,\nKouya turns toward the setting sun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5637-5639)
    "很短的，对问题的回答，洸哉转身面朝夕阳。\n阳光映入了他的眼睛，看起来很漂亮，\n[漏れ]也追随着洸哉视线的方向。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3340
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_1c2786ab:

    # "The light going into his eyes\nmakes them look beautiful.\nI follow suit, and turn my eyes too."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5639)
    "[漏れ]也追随着洸哉视线的方向。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3341
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_1a67a32f:

    # "Red streaks color the sky."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5641)
    "消失在对面那赤色的光，"

# game/day 15.rpy:3342
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_604db9a9:

    # "The red in the distance shifts to blue above us,\nand being reflected off the clouds in some places,{w=.2}\nit makes a fantastic scene."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5644-5646)
    "远处的红色向近处逐渐转换成蓝色，\n并且反射在各处漂浮的云朵上，\n制作出一片幻想的色调。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3343
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_f661c92d:

    # "It's somewhat nostalgic,\nlike a scenery you've known\nof since before you were born."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5648-5649)
    "总觉得有些怀念，\n似乎是在出生之前就知道的景象。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3344
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_80837334:

    # "I don't see this very often in the city.{p}The sky is narrow between the tall skyscrapers."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5651-5652)
    "在都市的时候也不大能看到这样的风景。\n高耸的楼阁使得天空变得狭小了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3345
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_c1fbb36c:

    # "Maybe because I'm not used to this,\nit feels extra nice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5654-5655)
    "是因为已经不常见到的原因吗，\n总觉得特别的漂亮。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3346
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_3de29298:

    # "But this is informing of the approaching night."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5657)
    "但是想到这预示着夜晚的到来，"

# game/day 15.rpy:3347
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_baa47001:

    # "When you think of it like that, it's something that\nconveys the fact that the day has begun to end,\nand that makes me feel a little sad."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5658-5659)
    "传达着一天的结束，\n就觉得十分寂寞。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3348
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_d058fcaf:

    # "Because of this feeling,\nI speak the words that are on my mind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5661)
    "是因为那样的心情吗，心中相称的感情脱口而出了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3349
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_65deaa9e:

    # fn "「If my vacation didn't end,\n I would be able to stay with everybody longer...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5663-5665)
    fn "「要是暑假永远不会结束，\n能一直和大家在一起就好了……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3350
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_1c1e739d:

    # "That way, I could make more memories.{p}Then I could be with everybody longer.{p}That's what I thought."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5667-5669)
    "这样的话，就能制造更多的回忆。\n还能和大家一直在一起。\n[漏れ]是这么想的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3351
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_7804bb1d:

    # "There would no longer be such a thing as\ninsufficient time, I could have as much fun with\neverybody as I want."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5671-5673)
    "时间不再是远远不够的东西，\n大家一起快乐地做着喜欢的事情。\n简直就如同梦一般。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3352
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_c964c650:

    # "It would be just like a dream."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5673)
    "简直就如同梦一般。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3356
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_257100e8:

    # ka "「Yeah...{p} That probably would be nice.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5678-5680)
    ka "「说的是呢……\n如果这样是多么好的事啊。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3357
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_93d8be34:

    # "Kouya also agrees with me.{p}However, there was a somewhat sad tone in his voice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5682-5683)
    "洸哉也赞成了[漏れ]的话。\n但是，那个语气有种莫名的悲伤。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3358
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_b89c2bb8:

    # "Even I know why.{w=.2} It's simple."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5685)
    "理由[漏れ]也明白。是很简单的东西。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3359
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_c0f42102:

    # "We both know it's nothing more than a dream.{p}It's something that could never happen."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5687-5688)
    "那是因为，这个假定正是「像梦一样的话」。\n这种事情在现实中是不存在的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3360
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_49d8164b:

    # "I know that too.{p}Because of that, Kouya doesn't say any more.\nI don't have anything to add after that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5690-5694)
    "这种事情[漏れ]也知道。\n正是因为知道，\n洸哉也不需要再多说什么。\n[漏れ]也没有，能跟在那句话之后的言辞。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3361
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_e86366eb:

    # "The silence flows naturally between us.\nI feel a slightly cold wind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5696-5697)
    "理所当然地，沉默在[漏れ]们之间流动。\n[漏れ]感觉到了风有点冷。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3362
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_393fac36:

    # ka "「You know...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5699-5700)
    ka "「……那个。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3363
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_7a6b29dd:

    # "After a while, Kouya begins to talk."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5702)
    "过了一会，洸哉打破了沉默。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3364
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_b5fb207e:

    # fn "「What?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5704-5705)
    fn "「什么？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3365
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_0652ae02:

    # ka "「Someday... Summer vacation is going to be over.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5707-5708)
    ka "「暑假是……总有结束的一天。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3366
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_68b66dff:

    # fn "「...Yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5710-5711)
    fn "「……嗯。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3367
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_3b8cbeae:

    # ka "「Then we should at least spend the remaining time\n together even more than we did before.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5713-5715)
    ka "「那么至少，在剩下的时间里\n更多地在一起吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3368
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_42306060:

    # ka "「If you do that, then you'll be\n able to make more memories.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5717-5718)
    ka "「那样做的话，一定能制造更多的回忆的。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3369
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_2577d38e:

    # "Kouya ruffles my hair.\nEven though they were only a few words,\nI understood his encouragement."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5720-5722)
    "洸哉揉了揉[漏れ]的头。\n虽然言语很少，但那是洸哉式的鼓励，\n这点[漏れ]是知道的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3370
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_13b03e0d:

    # "His concern makes me happy,\nas well as a little embarrassed."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5724)
    "对于他的关心[漏れ]很高兴，不知怎么的心里痒痒的。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3371
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_7c659639_1:

    # fn "「Kouya...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5726-5727)
    fn "「洸哉……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3372
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_ff258fd9:

    # ka "「When your vacation is over,\n the connection between us\n and your memories aren't going to disappear.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5729-5731)
    ka "「暑假结束了，并不表示我们的关系\n和回忆也消失了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3376
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_6e82e0fd:

    # ka "「So... You'll be all right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5736-5737)
    ka "「所以……没关系的。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3377
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_a763018c:

    # "Kouya gives a shy laugh as he says that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5739)
    "这样说着洸哉露出了腼腆的笑容。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3378
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_ed08b868:

    # "His smile clears away the depressed feelings I had.{p}I can feel energy seep into the depths of my heart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5741-5743)
    "那个笑容，将[漏れ]心中的阴霾\n全部吹走了。\n元气像要从心底溢出，那样子的感觉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3379
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_f757a1bf:

    # "I spontaneously smile and turn toward Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5745)
    "[漏れ]也自然地露出笑容，对洸哉答道。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3380
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_8074338a:

    # fn "「Yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5747-5748)
    fn "「――嗯。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3381
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_9145272e:

    # "He's right, it's nothing to worry about.{p}Just as he said, even if time passes,\nthis isn't going to disappear."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5750-5752)
    "是的，没什么可担心的。\n正如洸哉所说的，\n时间流逝消除不了的东西也有很多。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3382
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_5749e026:

    # "I had completely forgotten such an obvious thing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5754)
    "那样明显的答案，[漏れ]却完全忘记了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3383
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_7c3c2ee4:

    # "But the most important part, the basis, has not.{p}In this half of a month,\nI've thought about this countless times."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5756-5761)
    "时隔五年返回的这个村庄。\n确实[漏れ]们随着时间流逝逐渐成长，\n有了稍微改变也说不定。\n但是作为最重要的「根」的部分却没有任何变化。\n在这半个月里，[漏れ]已经很多次意识到这一点。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3384
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_fdadc457:

    # "If that's the case,\nI'm sure it will be this way in the future."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5763)
    "这样的话，今后也一定如此。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3385
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_39955183:

    # "If that's the case, then that's enough for me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5764)
    "这样的话，就足够了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3386
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_09fa294a:

    # ka "「We should get back soon. It's getting dark.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5766-5767)
    ka "「那，差不多该走了哦。天就要黑了。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3387
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_8ac491f5:

    # fn "「Okay!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5769-5770)
    fn "「嗯！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3388
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_c2860fa9:

    # "When he says that, Kouya heads back the way he came.{p}I follow behind him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5772-5773)
    "说着洸哉从刚才来的道路返回。\n[漏れ]也跟了上去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3389
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_bad206d0:

    # "'Then we should at least spend the remaining time\ntogether even more than we did before.'"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5775-5776)
    "『那么至少，在剩下的时间里\n更多地在一起吧。』"

# game/day 15.rpy:3390
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_0302b026:

    # "That's what Kouya said earlier.{p}While walking, I reflect upon it.{p}Then, I whisper in my mind:"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5778-5780)
    "洸哉刚才说过的话。\n一边走着，[漏れ]一边咬着牙想起那个。\n并在心中嘟囔着。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3391
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_kouya_f75368a7:

    # "Thank you, Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5782)
    "――谢谢你，洸哉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3402
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_9f672437:

    # "Everybody breaks away from the circle,{w=.2} leaving\nJuuichi-san standing alone.{w} For some reason, {w=.2}he stares\nat the remains of the campfire."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5791-5793)
    "在大家解散之后，柔一独自一个人站着，\n表情微妙地盯着营火剩下的残迹，\n在那儿发呆。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3403
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_b4aba15e:

    # "The burnt firewood is illuminated by the evening sun.{p}It glows a dull, {w=.2}fake orange that isn't from a flame.{p}The charcoal will probably never burn again, either."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5795-5797)
    "已经烧尽的薪柴，在夕阳的映照下，\n反射出了宛如虚假的火焰一般的橘红色光辉。\n这个木炭，也一样不可能在此燃烧起来了吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3404
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_8a262990:

    # "It seems to have proclaimed the end of our camping\ntrip. I feel an undescribable loneliness."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5799-5800)
    "感觉就像是在擅自宣告露营已经结束了似的，\n让[漏れ]不知怎地觉得寂寞了起来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3405
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_dcd82642:

    # "I wonder what Juuichi-san is looking at that's so\ninteresting."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5802)
    "柔一也是，看着那种东西会觉得有趣吗。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3406
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_fcc9051d:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san, {w=.2}what's the matter?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5804-5805)
    fn "「怎么了吗？　柔一。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3410
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_71d25957:

    # ju "「...[ln].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5810-5811)
    ju "「……[西村]。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3411
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_6b7f5070:

    # "He looks at me, {w=.2}then returns to staring at the\ncampfire."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5813)
    "柔一往这里撇了一眼，然后又再次转头回去盯着前方。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3415
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_5beb8cc5:

    # ju "「I'm just thinking about something.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5818-5819)
    ju "「稍微在想些事，唉。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3416
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_6d477a1d:

    # fn "「What's bothering you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5821-5822)
    fn "「是有什么烦恼吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3420
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_22f3b648:

    # ju "「...I wouldn't say it's bothering me.{p} I just remembered something from the past.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5826-5828)
    ju "「……到算不上是烦恼。\n只是些以前的事情，现在突然想起来了而已。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3421
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_364bccb1:

    # fn "「Was it when I was still living here?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5830-5831)
    fn "「在[漏れ]以前还待在这里的时候的事吗？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3422
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_aeca2ff7:

    # "He shakes his head."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5833)
    "柔一听到[漏れ]的问题后摇了摇头。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3426
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_3d4bc79c:

    # ju "「Not that far back.{p} It was about the time I started high school.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5837-5839)
    ju "「不是那么久以前的事。\n是差不多我刚上高中时发生的事。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3427
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_7bfa4e5e:

    # "I have no idea what it could be if that's the case..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5841-5842)
    "也就是说，是[漏れ]不会知道的事情\n的意思喽……"

# game/day 15.rpy:3428
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_78e67674:

    # "I can't fill that time I was away from everybody.{p}That doesn't mean it's my fault, {w=.2}or Juuichi-san's.{p}We were all just kids, {w=.2}it was beyond our control."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5844-5846)
    "无法简单地填补起来的，[漏れ]和大家之间的那段空白时间。\n这既不是[漏れ]的错，更不是柔一的错。\n对还是孩子的[漏れ]们来说，这也是无可奈何。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3429
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_d24529d5:

    # "But it still stings my heart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5848)
    "即使如此，还是会觉得胸口隐隐作痛。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3430
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_77f0417e:

    # fn "「I see...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5850-5851)
    fn "「那是……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3434
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_86df581d:

    # ju "「Sorry,{w=.2}\n but it doesn't have anything to do with you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5855-5856)
    ju "「抱歉，这是和[西村]无关的话题。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3435
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_99b1fe96:

    # "His expression is overtly stern.{p}There's no way I could pry any further than that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5858-5859)
    "柔一的表情明显地变得有些凶恶。\n更详细的情况看来是不可能跟[漏れ]说的样子。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3436
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_66109bca:

    # "...I'm sure it's something I can't just ask about out\nof curiosity."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5861-5862)
    "……肯定，不是那种能单纯为了有趣\n而说出来的话题吧。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3440
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_b61fc2aa:

    # ju "「...I'm sorry」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5866-5867)
    ju "「……抱歉。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3441
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_87c503e4:

    # fn "「No, that's fine.{p} I was just being too nosy.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5869-5871)
    fn "「不，没关系啦。\n是[漏れ]太随便了才对。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3442
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_e92e7fc0:

    # "Things have gotten awkward.{p}With that, Juuichi-san stays silent."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5873-5874)
    "跟着说出来的这些话也变得有些生硬。\n也因此，柔一便沉默了下去。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3443
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_74f5cc00:

    # "Him staring at the former bonfire is unusual.{p}It's like he's there in body but not in spirit."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5876-5877)
    "一直看着残余营火的柔一，\n和往常的他不太一样，有种心不在此处的气氛。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3444
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_f256e063:

    # "I should say something.{p}But my thoughts keep going in circles.{p}It's caught in my throat and won't come out easily."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5879-5881)
    "不知道该说什么。\n可是，脑袋里却忍不住一直在想着这事。\n喉咙深处感觉痒痒的，却无法将它宣泄出来。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3445
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_5dc20f21:

    # fn "「Um, {w=.2}Juuichi-san...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5883-5884)
    fn "「那个，柔一……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3446
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_b7a2aa48:

    # ta "「Heey, {w=.2}what're you guys doing!?{p} Get in the truck already!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5886-5888)
    ta "「喂——你们两个在那里干嘛啊！\n快点过来给我上车了啦——！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3447
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_b71be5f1:

    # "Just as I nervously speak to him,{w=.2}\nTatsu-nii yells over me.{p}...That was really bad timing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5890-5892)
    "[漏れ]正吞吞吐吐地打算向柔一提问的，\n却突然被辰兄的大喊给打断了。\n……真的是时机很不巧呢。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3451
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_d396f404:

    # ju "「...[ln], {w=.2}let's go.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5897-5898)
    ju "「……[西村]，我们走吧。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3452
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_e64758db:

    # fn "「Oh, {w=.2}yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5900-5901)
    fn "「啊，好。」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3453
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_1ecbc7e3:

    # "He begins to walk briskly towards the truck.{p}I too head towards everybody."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5903-5904)
    "说完后，柔一便快步往卡车的方向\n赶了过去。[漏れ]也跟着一起走向大家的身边。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3457
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_juuichi_6ecaaf94:

    # "Juuichi-san's orange-dyed back walking fowards{w=.2}\n-the back that always looks so strong-{p}now looks weaker than usual to me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5909-5911)
    "在前面走着，染上了橘红色的柔一的背影\n——那个看起来一直都很高大宽广的背影——\n在[漏れ]的眼中，似乎比平常还来得细小了许多。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3468
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shin_4bd3ccab:

    # "I found Shin-kun looking pensively at the sunset."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5918)
    "在黄昏之下，深正恍惚地向远方眺望。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3472
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shin_4a358c8e:

    # fn "「What are you doing?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5923-5924)
    fn "「在做什么？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3473
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_shin_7a62cebf:

    # "Hearing my voice, Shin-kun looks at me for a moment.\nLooking briefly back at the sky,\nhe speaks to me in his usual tone."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/キャンプ02.ks (KS 5926-5928)
