translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_3c57c43c:

    # "That's true.{w} There are times when I feel like this.{w} The dusk around me is even deepening my thoughts."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 984)
    "没错，[漏れ]有时候也会有这种感觉。[l]而且黄昏的时刻又加深了这样的感觉。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3649
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_dba3df45:

    # to "「... Hmm ...{w} What do you mean?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 989)
    to "「……嗯～[l]啊～[l]在说什么啊？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3653
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_a6d3f5b5:

    # to "「For the last half month, we all got excited at the\n welcome party, we all went to the beach to play,\n and we all went camping today.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 993)
    to "「这半个月，欢迎会办得很热烈，跟大家一起去海边玩，今天也来露营」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3654
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_6c57236c:

    # to "「Everyday is wonderful and I had a lot of fun.{p} Didn't you have fun, too?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 997)
    to "「每天都过得很充实，我真的很开心。[l]那么[博行]也一样吧？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3655
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_bce6a171:

    # fn "「Yeah ...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1002)
    fn "「嗯……」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3656
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_c2b9047b:

    # to "「Well then, I'm sure that everyday of the half month\n left will be just as enjoyable as everyday that we\n had, starting from tomorrow.」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1005)
    to "「那样的话，从明天起的半个月，每天一定能够感受到相同的快乐」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3660
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_4f2f4cbf:

    # to "「You still have half a month to spend and have fun\n with everyone!」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1010)
    to "「与大家一起度过最愉快的每一天，就用剩下的半个月实现」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3664
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_11fc388c:

    # to "「No, not just half a month.{w} There's a winter\n vacation in the winter.{w} There's a spring vacation\n in the spring.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1015)
    to "「不，不只半个月。[l]冬天来的时候会有寒假，[l]春天来的时候会有春假」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3665
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_458d8b17:

    # to "「Then you could go back to Minasato again.{w} If you\n want, you can even move back here.{w} This will always\n be your hometown.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1019)
    to "「然后再回到村里来不就好了吗？[l]你可以再搬回来。[l]这里永远是你的家哦」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3669
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_91c85023:

    # to "「Our best days will continue even after this summer,\n right?{w} Aren't you looking forward to it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1025)
    to "「我们最好的一天，将在今年夏天结束后一直持续下去吧？[l]呐？」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3670
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_606f5c47:

    # "He puts his hands on my shoulders."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1029)
    "这么说着，轻轻地把手放在[漏れ]的肩膀上。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3671
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_965131a1:

    # fn "「To-Torahiko ...{w} Thank you ...{w} I feel much\n better now.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1032)
    fn "「虎彦……[l]谢谢……[l]稍微有点精神了」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3672
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_93dba8e4:

    # fn "「... You are really good at encouraging people.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1035)
    fn "「……虎彦，真的很擅长鼓励人呢」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3676
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_adc6eb0d:

    # to "「Hah!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1039)
    to "「就～是啊」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3677
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_dd03e445:

    # "Torahiko gives me a big smile."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1041)
    "虎彦转过身来笑容满面。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3681
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_ca51cc78:

    # to "「Well, I just tell you the best things!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1045)
    to "「嘛，[l]我最想说的是，船到桥头自然直！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3682
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_15b4e698:

    # ta "「Hey!{w} What are you doing?{w} I'm leaving you\n two behind!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1048)
    ta "「喂——！[l]在干嘛啊？[l]要走了喔——」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3686
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_c7eefb45:

    # to "「Seems like Tatsu-nii is calling.{w} Let's go, [fn]!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1052)
    to "「辰兄在叫了。[l]来，走吧」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3687
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_2ed1eff0:

    # fn "「You're right!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1055)
    fn "「嗯！」"

# game/day 15.rpy:3691
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_af7068cb:

    # "Torahiko's back, which I saw when I followed him from behind, seems to be much more reliable than when he was a kid."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1059)
    "当[漏れ]跟在后面时，看到了虎彦的背影，感觉比小时候看到的还要可靠。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3692
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_644f3210:

    # "I seem to have been overtaken by Torahiko the whole time I was in the city."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1062)
    "[漏れ]在城市生活的这段时间，虎彦似乎已经超过[漏れ]很多了。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3693
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_a9c19e16:

    # "Next time, it'll be my turn to overtake.{w} I can't stop thinking about it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1065)
    "现在是时候让[漏れ]超越了，[l]可不能停滞不前哪。"

# game/day 15.rpy:3694
translate chinese_simplified camp15_confess_torahiko_6c70aa4e:

    # "That my fun days with everyone will continue forever."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/torahiko/15日目.ks (KS 1068)
    "在未来直到永远，大家的快乐时光将一直继续下去。"

